l-agora-tv-strand-diverse-1235774105%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fthessaloniki-festival-agora-tv-strand-diverse-1235774105%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fthessaloniki-festival-agora-tv-strand-diverse-1235774105%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Firms%20Can%20Now%20List%20Directly%20On%20Foreign%20Stock%20Exchanges%3A%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20move%2C%20the%20government%20has%20permitted%20Indian%20companies%20to%20list%20on%20foreign%20exchanges%2C%20subject%20to%20certain%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20corporate%20affairs%20ministry%20has%20notified%20the%20relevant%20section%20under%20the%20companies%20law%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20overseas%20listings%20by%20local%20listed%20entities%20are%20carried%20out%20through%20American%20Depository%20Receipts%20(ADRs)%20and%20Global%20Depository%20Receipts%20(GDRs).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20exercise%20of%20the%20powers%20conferred%20by%20sub-section%20(2)%20of%20section%201%20of%20the%20Companies%20(Amendment)%20Act%2C%202020%20(29%20of%202020)%2C%20the%20Central%20Government%20hereby%20appoints%20the%2030th%20day%20of%20October%202023%20as%20the%20date%20on%20which%20the%20provisions%20of%20section%205%20of%20the%20said%20Act%20shall%20come%20into%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20notification%20on%20October%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20rules%20for%20direct%20overseas%20listing%20of%20Indian%20companies%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20notified.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESection%205%20allows%20certain%20classes%20of%20public%20companies%20to%20list%20their%20securities%20on%20permitted%20stock%20exchanges%20in%20permissible%20foreign%20jurisdictions%20or%20such%20other%20jurisdictions%2C%20as%20may%20be%20prescribed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2013%2C%20a%20senior%20government%20official%20said%20the%20ministry%20was%20looking%20at%20various%20aspects%2C%20including%20the%20possible%20eligibility%20criteria%2C%20to%20prepare%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20direct%20overseas%20listing%20of%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2028%2C%20Finance%20and%20Corporate%20Affairs%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said%20the%20government%20has%20decided%20to%20allow%20domestic%20companies%20to%20list%20overseas%20to%20help%20them%20access%20capital%20from%20the%20world%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202020%2C%20the%20move%20was%20announced%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Covid%20relief%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20government%20official%2C%20on%20July%2028%2C%20said%20that%20initially%2C%20the%20plan%20is%20to%20allow%20companies%20to%20list%20at%20the%20International%20Financial%20Services%20Centre%20in%20GIFT%20City%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20and%20later%2C%20they%20can%20list%20in%20any%20of%20the%20eight%20to%20nine%20specified%20overseas%20jurisdictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(Sebi)%20had%20previously%20recommended%20a%20framework%20within%20which%20such%20direct%20listing%20will%20be%20facilitated%2C%20and%20it%20is%20expected%20that%20the%20Sebi%20framework%20will%20be%20the%20basis%20for%20future%20regulation%20in%20this%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESebi%20had%20proposed%20allowing%20listings%20on%20stock%20exchanges%20in%20ten%20%26quot%3Bpermissible%20jurisdictions%26quot%3B%20with%20strong%20anti-money%20laundering%20regulations%2C%20including%20the%20NYSE%2C%20Nasdaq%2C%20the%20LSE%20and%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20along%20with%20other%20major%20exchanges%20in%20Japan%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20France%2C%20Germany%2C%20Switzerland%20and%20Canada.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698835