ent%20was%20committed%20to%20providing%20reservation%20for%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20gave%20a%2040-day%20deadline%20to%20the%20government%20to%20implement%20reservation%20for%20the%20Marathas%2C%20which%20it%20did%20not%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20before%20he%20ended%20his%20first%20strike%2C%20the%20state%20government%20announced%20its%20intention%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fthose-with-nizam-era-documents-recognising-them-as-kunbis-to-get-caste-certificates-cm-shindee%5C%22%3Eprovide%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20those%20who%20possessed%20relevant%20documentation%20from%20the%20pre-Independence%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20formed%20a%20five-member%20committee%20headed%20by%20retired%20Bombay%20high%20court%20judge%20Justice%20Sandeep%20Shinde%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmaratha-reservation-panel-to-submit-report-on-kunbi-caste-certificates-within-30-days%5C%22%3Eto%20study%20the%20process%20of%20issuing%20these%20certificates%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fkunbi-tag-marathas-5-member-committee-two-month-extension-dec-24-9002585%2F%5C%22%3Ereceived%20a%20two-month%20extension%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Sunday%20(October%2030)%20for%20finalising%20the%20process%2C%20although%20it%20has%20submitted%20a%20first%20report%20to%20the%20government%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fwire-updates%2Fnational%2F2023%2F10%2F31%2Fbom33-mh-quota-ld-cabinet.html%5C%22%3Ewhich%20accepted%20it%20on%20Tuesday%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%E2%80%99s%20cabinet%20announced%20that%20it%20has%20already%20begun%20the%20process%20of%20issuing%20Kunbi%20certificates%20to%20eligible%20Marathas%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Jarange-Patil%20has%20said%20that%20all%20members%20of%20the%20Maratha%20community%20must%20receive%20these%20certificates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-maharashtra-itll-be-open-season-until-the-2024-lok-sabha-election%5C%22%3EIn%20Maharashtra%2C%20It%E2%80%99ll%20Be%20Open%20Season%20Until%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20Election%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20a%20blanket%20reservation%20for%20Marathas.%20Marathas%20and%20Kunbis%20are%20the%20same%20as%20they%20share%20the%20same%20primary%20occupation%20which%20is%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fothers%2Fstate-averse-to-all-marathas-as-obcs-101698781100805.html%5C%22%3Estate%20cabinet%20decided%20against%20including%20all%20Marathas%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20reservations%20for%20Kunbis%20as%20it%20of%20the%20view%20that%20this%20is%20untenable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20demand%20for%20inclusion%20of%20all%20Marathas%20in%20OBC%20category%20is%20impossible%20and%20will%20grossly%20disturb%20the%20OBC%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20quoted%20an%20unnamed%20minister%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CApart%20from%20the%20reservation%20in%20jobs%20and%20education%2C%20the%20OBCs%20also%20get%20political%20reservation%2C%20and%20the%20inclusion%20of%20Marathas%20in%20this%20quota%20will%20elicit%20a%20sharp%20reaction%20from%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20OBC%20leaders%20in%20the%20state%20have%20said%20that%20though%20they%20were%20not%20against%20reservations%20for%20the%20Marathas%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fexplainer-why-the-maratha-quota-agitation-has-put-successive-maharashtra-governments-in-a-bind%5C%22%3Ethey%20would%20oppose%20measures%20that%20would%20encroach%20on%20their%20share%20of%20the%20pie%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bombay%20high%20court%20granted%2013%25%20and%2012%25%20reservation%20to%20the%20Marathas%20in%20government%20jobs%20and%20education%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmaratha-quota-case-sc-declares-reservation-over-50-as-unconstitutional%5C%22%3Equashed%20the%20reservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021%2C%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Creservation%20cannot%20cross%20the%2050%25%20limit%20in%20states%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMarathas%20are%20estimated%20to%20constitute%20over%2033%25%20of%20the%20state%20population%20and%20enjoy%20political%20dominance%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20state%20in%201960%2C%2012%20out%20of%2020%20chief%20ministers%20belonged%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20agitators%20have%20said%20that%20these%20privileges%20are%20enjoyed%20only%20by%20a%20handful%20of%20families%20and%20that%20most%20of%20the%20community%20continues%20to%20be%20marginalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698834919000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26132749%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-1.27.15-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finternet-suspended-in-marathwada-districts-jarange-patil-threatens-to-quit-water%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Wednesday%2C%20an%20%E2%80%98all-party%E2%80%99%20meeting%20convened%20by%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20to%20discuss%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20agitation%20began%20in%20Mumbai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finternet-suspended-in-marathwada-districts-jarange-patil-threatens-to-quit-water%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Khushi%20aces%20the%20midi-dress%20look%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%