-peter-stoinis-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMarcus%20Stoinis%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20replace%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaxwell%20is%20indispensable%20to%20Australia's%20team%2C%20especially%20since%20soaring%20to%20form%20by%20scoring%20a%2040-ball%20100%20against%20the%20Netherlands%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Even%20in%20the%20last%20World%20Cup%20match%20against%20New%20Zealand%2C%20Maxwell%20scored%20a%2024-ball%2041%20as%20his%20team%20strengthened%20its%20position%20in%20the%20semi-final%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20transporting%20him%20back%20from%20the%20clubhouse%20to%20the%20team%20bus%2C%20Glenn%20Maxwell%20came%20off%20the%20back%20of%20a%20car%20and%20has%20suffered%20a%20small%20concussion%2C%20so%20he%20will%20go%20into%20concussion%20protocols%20for%20the%20next%20period%20of%20time%20and%20will%20unfortunately%20miss%20the%20England%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Australian%20coach%20Andrew%20McDonald%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere'll%20be%20no%20replacement%20(in%20the%20squad)%20as%20such%2C%20he'll%20go%20into%20six%20to%20eight%20days%20concussion%20protocol.%20So%20they%20said%20that%20takes%20into%20account%20the%20England%20game%2C%20he'll%20be%20unavailable%20for%20that%20game.%20And%20then%20clearly%20within%20the%20squad%20we've%20got%20some%20players%20who%20become%20available%20Marcus%20Stoinis%2C%20Cameron%20Green's%20there%20available%20as%20well%2C%20but%20we%20haven't%20made%20that%20decision%20as%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurther%20explaining%20the%20incident%2C%20McDonald%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20guys%20were%20ferried%20off%20on%20carts.%20Glenn%20and%20a%20few%20other%20players%20jumped%20on%20the%20back%20of%20carts%20and%20unfortunately%20he%20lost%20his%20grip%20on%20the%20way%20back%20to%20the%20team%20bus%20and%20sustained%20that%20injury.%20Over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20days%20he's%20been%20assessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20feel%20as%20though%20it'll%20be%20a%20relatively%20straightforward%20return%20to%20play%20protocol%20with%20where%20he's%20at%20at%20the%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAustralia%20have%20won%204%20matches%20on%20the%20bounce%2C%20after%20losing%20the%20first%202%2C%20and%20are%20in%20a%20solid%20position%20to%20secure%20one%20of%20the%20top%204%20spots.%20After%20the%20England%20clash%2C%20they%20are%20scheduled%20to%20take%20on%20giant-killers%20Afghanistan%20on%20November%2007.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698834480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F9i5fsnb8_glenn-maxwell_625x300_01_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fglenn-maxwell-injured-in-freak-golf-accident-to-miss-england-match-due-to-concussion-4534806%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Glenn%20Maxwell%20will%20miss%20Australia's%20World%20Cup%20match%20against%20England%2C%20having%20suffered%20concussion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fglenn-maxwell-injured-in-freak-golf-accident-to-miss-england-match-due-to-concussion-4534806%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fglenn-maxwell-injured-in-freak-golf-accident-to-miss-england-match-due-to-concussion-4534806%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fglenn-maxwell-injured-in-freak-golf-accident-to-miss-england-match-due-to-concussion-4534806%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tarantula%20Causes%20Vehicle%20Crash%20In%20California%2C%20Motorcyclist%20Hospitalised%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20tourist%20was%20injured%20in%20California's%20Death%20Valley%20National%20Park%20in%20an%20accident%20caused%20by%20a%20tarantula.%20The%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20the%20National%20Park%20Service%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20accident%20took%20place%20on%20October%2028%20after%20a%20Swiss%20couple%20travelling%20on%20a%20state%20highway%20in%20a%20camper%20applied%20brakes%20to%20avoid%20hitting%20the%20spider.%20The%20van%20overturned%20and%20fell%20on%20the%2024-year-old%20Canadian%20motorcyclist%2C%20who%20was%20injured.%20The%20spider%20survived%20the%20pile-up%2C%20escaping%20into%20the%20desert%20unharmed%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20motorcyclist%20was%20taken%20to%20Desert%20View%20Hospital%20in%20the%20nearby%20town%20of%20Pahrump.%20His%20condition%20is%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67262792%5C%22%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20Superintendent%20Mike%20Reynolds%20was%20the%20first%20park%20service%20employee%20to%20reach%20the%20scene%20of%20the%20accident%20and%20asked%20other%20visitors%20to%20the%20park%20to%20drive%20slowly%20in%20the%20area%2C%20particularly%20when%20going%20down%20steep%20hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fcalifornia%2Fstory%2F2023-10-31%2Fdesert-tarantula-causes-two-car-accident-in-death-valley%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELos%20Angeles%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20Swiss%20tourists%20were%20%26quot%3Bfine%26quot%3B.%20Meanwhile%2C%20park%20spokesperson%20Abby%20Wines%20said%20the%20biker's%20injuries%20were%20%26quot%3Bnon-life-threatening%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20is%20unusual%20because%20it%20is%20very%20rare%20to%20find%20a%20tarantula%20above%20the%20ground.%20According%20to%20park%20officials%2C%20these%20spiders%20spend%20most%20of%20their%20time%20underground.%20They%20also%20said%20that%20the%20eight-legged%20creature%20is%20slow%20moving%20and%20non-aggressive%2C%20adding%20that%20their%20non-poisonous%20bite%20is%20%26quot%3Bsimilar%20to%20a%20bee%20sting%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThings%20to%20know%20about%20tarantulas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnh.org%2Fexplore%2Fnews-blogs%2Fon-exhibit-posts%2Ften-things-to-know-about-tarantulas%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Museum%20of%20Natural%20History%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20tarantulas%20average%20five%20inches%20long%20but%20have%20leg%20spans%20of%20up%20to%2011%20inches.%20The%20museum%20further%20said%20that%20tarantulas%20make%20up%20about%20two%20per%20cent%20of%20the%2044%2C500%20known%20species%20of%20spiders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20spider%20does%20produce%20venom%20that%20is%20toxic%20to%20its%20prey%20-%20insects%2C%20small%20frogs%2C%20lizards%2C%20and%20mice%20-%20but%20it's%20not%20a%20threat%20to%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tarantulas%20are%20also%20pets%20among%20popular%20spider%20lovers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698834480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F58i1ipv8_tarantula_625x300_28_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftarantula-causes-vehicle-crash-in-california-motorcyclist-hospitalised-4534963%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20incident%20is%20unusual%20because%20it%20is%20very%20rare%20to%20find%20a%20tarantula%20above%20the%20ground.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftarantula-causes-vehicle-crash-in-california-motorcyclist-hospitalised-4534963%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftarantula-causes-vehicle-crash-in-california-motorcyclist-hospitalised-4534963%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftarantula-causes-vehicle-crash-in-california-motorcyclist-hospitalised-4534963%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20'Three%20Criminal%20Law%20Bills%20Will%20Establish%20Permanent%20Extra-Constitutional%20Emergency%20Powers'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01154144%2FSravasti.00_35_21_13.Still002-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2011%2C%202023%20the%20Union%20Government%20introduced%20three%20new%20Bills%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20replace%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%201860%20(the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20Bill)%20the%20Indian%20Evidence%20Act%2C%201872%20(the%20Bharatiya%20Sakshya%20Adhiniyam%20Bill)%20and%20the%20Criminal%20Procedure%20Code%2C%201973%20(the%20Bharatiya%20Nagarik%20Suraksha%20Sanhita%20Bill).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EG.%20Mohan%20Gopal%2C%20advocate%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20and%20a%20legal%20academician%2C%20sits%20down%20to%20discuss%20the%20changes%20being%20brought%20through%20these%20bills%20and%20what%20they%20imply%20for%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20while%20quantitatively%2C%20the%20bills%20only%20change%20some%2020%25-25%25%20of%20the%20law%20in%20the%20three%20current%20statutes%3B%20what%20is%20crucial%20and%20requires%20very%20close%20public%20attention%2C%20are%20a%20dozen%20chilling%20changes%20to%20the%20law%20that%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20liquidate%20liberty%2C%20decimate%20democracy%20and%20fundamentally%20change%20the%20face%20of%20our%20polity%20from%20democratic%20to%20authoritarian%20should%20the%20government%20decide%20to%20deploy%20any%20or%20all%20of%20these%20changes%20to%20their%20fullest%20extent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FnpHbecvfc9o%3Fsi%3DBkjeuJQPk5xNfw7k%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698834319000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01154144%2FSravasti.00_35_21_13.Still002-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcriminal-law-bills-explained-g-mohan-gopal%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22G.%20Mohan%20Gopal%2C%20advocate%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%2C