am%20home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Background%3A%20a%20derelict%20house%20in%20Scotland%2C%20Foreground%3A%20Claire%20Segeren%20and%20her%20partner.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65412e23284fe8aac5234222%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20millennial%20couple%20bought%20this%20crumbling%20house%20in%20the%20Scottish%20Highlands%20without%20seeing%20it.%3Cp%3EClaire%20Segeren%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EClaire%20Segeren%20and%20her%20boyfriend%20bought%20a%20Victorian%20house%20in%20the%20Scottish%20Highlands%20by%20accident.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20bid%20on%20the%20wrong%20property%20in%20an%20auction%20and%20spent%20four%20years%20renovating%20the%20derelict%20house.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20couple%20now%20live%20on%20the%20property%20full%20time%20and%20rent%20out%20the%20apartments%20as%20vacation%20rentals.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20article%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Claire%20Segeren%2C%20a%2029-year-old%20neuroscience%20graduate%20from%20Canada%20who%20bought%20and%20renovated%20a%20derelict%20Victorian%20villa%20in%20Scotland%20with%20her%20partner%2C%20Cal%20Hunter.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20partner%20and%20I%20are%20builders%20who%20plan%20to%20work%20on%20property%20projects%20after%20restoring%20our%20crumbling%20Victorian%20villa%20in%20the%20Scottish%20countryside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20accidentally%20bought%20a%20crumbling%20Victorian%20villa%20at%20an%20auction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dunoon%20House%2C%20a%20derelict%20house%20in%20the%20Scottish%20Highlands%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654113da96f7540cd06a373c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20were%20shocked%20when%20they%20saw%20the%20villa%20in%20person.%3Cp%3EClaire%20Segeren%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20I%20was%20a%2024-year-old%20neuroscience%20graduate%20from%20Canada%20and%20had%20my%20sights%20set%20on%20studying%20medicine.%20I%20planned%20on%20moving%20to%20the%20UK%20after%20receiving%20an%20offer%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Glasgow%20School%20of%20Medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20boyfriend%2C%20Cal%2C%20was%20a%2026-year-old%20carpenter%20from%20Hull%2C%20England.%20We'd%20met%20working%20in%20the%20French%20Alps.%20Buying%20a%20property%20in%20Glasgow%20was%20originally%20going%20to%20be%20a%20project%20for%20him%20to%20work%20on%20while%20I%20studied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22821%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Claire%20Segeren%20and%20her%20partner%20at%20their%20house%20in%20Scotland%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654114a596f7540cd06a37f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221228%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClaire%20Segeren%20and%20Cal%3Cp%3EJoshua%20Sivarajah%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20against%20medical%20school%20because%20of%20the%20high%20tuition%2C%20but%20we%20still%20wanted%20to%20buy%20an%20affordable%20property%20to%20fix%20up%20and%20sell.%20We%20settled%20on%20a%20fire-damaged%20apartment%20in%20Glasgow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20in%20Canada%20recovering%20from%20shoulder%20surgery%20when%20Cal%20returned%20to%20the%20UK%20and%20traveled%20to%20Scotland%20to%20put%20a%20bid%20in%20on%20the%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECal%20was%20following%20the%20bids%20with%20an%20auction%20booklet.%20Unbeknownst%20to%20him%2C%20a%20new%20property%20was%20added%20just%20before%20the%20Glasgow%20apartment%20that%20wasn't%20in%20the%20booklet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20bid%20on%20the%20new%20property%20thinking%20it%20was%20the%20Glasgow%20one.%20We%20expected%20a%20lot%20of%20competition%2C%20so%20when%20nobody%20else%20bid%20against%20him%2C%20he%20knew%20something%20was%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECal%20realized%20we%20had%20just%20bought%20an%20apartment%20in%20Jameswood%20Villa%3A%20a%20four-apartment%20property%20in%20the%20coastal%20village%20of%20Sandbank%2C%20just%20north%20of%20Dunoon%20in%20the%20Scottish%20Highlands.%20We%20bid%20%C2%A310%2C000%2C%20or%20about%20%2412%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224752%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20derelict%20house%20in%20Scotland.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65411548284fe8aac52300da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223168%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrom%20the%20auction%20brochure%2C%20the%20couple%20weren't%20too%20concernd%3Cp%3EClaire%20Segeren%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20left%20the%20auction%20in%20a%20panic%20and%20called%20me.%20I%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20the%20worst%20that%20can%20happen%3F%20We%20just%20got%20a%20property%20for%20%C2%A310%2C000.%20It's%20not%20the%20end%20of%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%20The%20property%20in%20the%20brochure%20didn't%20look%20that%20bad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20property%20was%20derelict%20and%20nothing%20like%20the%20pictures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224752%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Derelict%20house%20in%20Scotland%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654116bf356802a56be86d71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223168%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20house%20was%20derelict%20and%20needed%20gutting.%3Cp%3EClaire%20Segeren%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECal%20went%20to%20look%20at%20Jameswood%20Villa%20the%20next%20week%20in%20person%2C%20and%20the%20real%20worry%20set%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pictures%20on%20the%20brochure%20were%2010%20years%20old%20and%20hid%20a%20partially%20collapsing%20front%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224608%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Derelict%20Dunoon%20House%20in%20Scotland%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6541179896f7540cd06a3de2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20renovation%20was%20a%20passion%20project%20for%20the%20couple.%3Cp%3EClaire%20Segeren%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20roof%20had%20been%20leaking%20for%2020%20to%2025%20years.%20Rot%2C%20water%20damage%2C%20and%20mold%20were%20everywhere.%20We'd%20have%20to%20build%20a%20new%20house%20inside%20the%20old%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20to%20ask%20ourselves%20whether%20we%20would%20cut%20our%20losses%20or%20pour%20everything%20into%20this%20as%20a%20passion%20project.%20What%20encouraged%20us%20to%20take%20the%20leap%20was%20that%20we%20both%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20gorgeous%20surroundings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20stood%20in%20the%20Scottish%20highlands.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65411738356802a56be86e4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20dramatic%20Scottish%20landscape.%3Cp%3EClaire%20Segeren%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20set%20out%20to%20buy%20the%20remaining%20apartments.%20It%20took%20us%20six%20months%20to%20find%20the%20original%20owners%20of%20the%20three%20other%20apartments%20and%20buy%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20our%20best%20chance%20to%20get%20on%20the%20property%20ladder%2C%20and%20the%20size%20of%20the%20house%20meant%20we%20could%20live%20in%20it%20while%20renting%20out%20the%20other%20apartments.%20This%20income%20could%20help%20cover%20the%20renovation%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECosts%20of%20the%20renovation%20project%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20couple%20standing%20outside%20a%20renovated%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65411c98284fe8aac5231456%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221984%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20renovated%20exterior%20of%20the%20villa.%3Cp%3EClaire%20Segeren%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20cost%20%C2%A340%2C000%20altogether%20to%20buy%20the%20whole%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20some%20savings%20but%20initially%20borrowed%20money%20from%20my%20parents%20to%20help%20buy%20the%20apartments%20and%20start%20our%20renovations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20proposed%20a%20plan%20of%20the%20costs%2C%20timescale%2C%20and%20estimated%20final%20value%20and%20wrote%20up%20an%20agreement.%20My%20parents%20didn't%20need%20persuading%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0they%20knew%20Cal%20and%20I%20were%20both%20hard-working%20and%20could%20be%20held%20accountable.%20We%20will%20pay%20it%20back%20through%20our%20building%20work%2C%20as%20well%20as%20income%20from%20renting%20out%20two%20of%20the%20apartments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22renovated%20kitchens%20in%20a%20refurbished%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654121d5356802a56be888e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20renovated%20kitchens%20in%20two%20of%20the%20villa's%20apartments.%3Cp%3EClaire%20Segeren%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20estimated%20it%20would%20take%20two%20years%20to%20renovate%20and%20cost%20between%20%C2%A3100%2C000%20and%20%C2%A3120%2C000%20to%20get%20it%20to%20a%20liveable%20standard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20renovation%20ended%20up%20taking%20four%20years.%20It%20cost%20about%20%C2%A3120%2C000%20in%20the%20end%2C%20but%20that's%20cheap%20for%20a%20project%20this%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20front%20room%20of%20a%20renovated%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6541227496f7540cd06a5ac0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20completed%20front%20room%20in%20the%20Scottish%20villa.%3Cp%3EClaire%20Segeren%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20did%20everything%20ourselves%20to%20keep%20costs%20down.%20We%20paid%20for%20only%20one%20week%20of%20professional%20help%2C%20reclaimed%20as%20many%20materials%20as%20possible%20from%20the%20site%2C%20found%20deals%20on%20eBay%20and%20Gumtree%2C%20and%20collaborated%20with%20brands%20using%20our%20Instagram%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20lived%20out%20of%20a%20%24610%20camper%20van%20on%20the%20project%20site%20for%204%20years%20to%20keep%20our%20costs%20down%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221392%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20young%20couple%20sitting%20outside%20a%20camper%20van.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65411814284fe8aac5230822%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22930%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESegeren%20and%20her%20partner%20lived%20in%20a%20tiny%20camper%20van%20for%20four%20years.%3Cp%3EJoshua%20Sivarajah%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECal%20and%20I%20weren't%20employed%20when%20we%20bought%20Jameswood%20Villa.%20He%20was%20freelancing%20and%20taking%20on%20projects%20as%20they%20came%20up%2C%20and%20I%20started%20working%20at%20a%20restaurant%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20knew%20we%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20renovate%20the%20villa%20and%20rent%20another%20property%2C%20so%20we%20bought%20a%20tiny%20camper%20for%20%C2%A3500%2C%20parked%20it%20at%20the%20villa%2C%20and%20lived%20there%20for%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20tough%2C%20but%20it%20kept%20our%20living%20costs%20down.%20During%20the%20build%2C%20I%20worked%20on%20the%20property%20full%20time%20during%20the%20day%20and%20as%20a%20bartender%20in%20the%20evenings.%20Cal%20would%20take%20months%20off%20from%20the%20project%20for%20paid%20carpentry%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224608%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20and%20a%20woman%20sat%20around%20a%20table%20in%20a%20derelict%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65411882284fe8aac523096f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESegeren%20said%20they%20invited%20friends%20to%20come%20and%20see%20the%20house.%3Cp%3EClaire%20Segeren%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20lived%20frugally%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20to%20keep%20overhead%20low.%20It%20meant%20saying%20no%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20fun%20things%2C%20including%20traveling%2C%20going%20to%20festivals%2C%20and%20even%20just%20going%20to%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20made%20our%20own%20fun%2C%20inviting%20our%20friends%20over%20and%20exploring%20the%20area.%20It%20was%20an%20amazing%20part%20of%20our%20lives%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0just%20different%20from%20what%20we%20were%20doing%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20opened%20up%20part%20of%20the%20house%20as%20vacation%20rentals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERenting%20out%20the%20other%20apartments%20made%20sense%20because%20the%20villa%20was%20too%20big%20for%20two%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20long-term%20tenants%20wouldn't%20give%20us%20the%20flexibility%20to%20invite%20friends%20and%20family%20over%20during%20the%20holidays%2C%20so%20we%20settled%20on%20making%20it%20a%20holiday%20rental.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Left%3A%20a%20newly%20renovated%20bathroom%2C%20right%3A%20a%20newly%20renovated%20bedroom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654122eb96f7540cd06a5bc4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20newly%20renovated%20interior%20of%20the%20Dunoon%2C%20Scotland%2C%20house.%3Cp%3EClaire%20Segeren%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20beautiful%20area%20and%20a%20great%20location%20for%20a%20holiday.%20The%20income%20from%20a%20short-term%20rental%20was%20a%20great%20way%20to%20pay%20off%20some%20of%20the%20project's%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20letting%20it%20out%20in%20September.%20We%20charge%20%C2%A3125%20a%20night%20for%20a%20two-bedroom%20apartment%20that%20sleeps%20four.%20We%20were%20nervous%20about%20opening%20offseason%2C%20but%20because%20of%20the%20success%20of%20our%20social-media%20channels%2C%20we've%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20support%20from%20fans%20booking%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20newly%20renovated%20interior%20of%20a%20Scottish%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6541238696f7540cd06a5cb5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20couple%20live%20in%20the%20house%20while%20renting%20out%20an%20apartment%20as%20a%20short-term%20rental.%3Cp%3EClaire%20Segeren%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20experience%20is%20not%20some%20'get%20rich%20quick'%20scheme%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECal%20could%20have%20made%20more%20as%20a%20carpenter%2C%20and%20I%20could've%20started%20a%20job%20with%20my%20neuroscience%20degree.%20But%20once%20we%20saw%20this%20house%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20our%20home%20because%20we%20knew%20we%20could%20make%20something%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20worked%20six%20days%20a%20week%20on%20this%20project%20for%20four%20years.%20Now%20we%20have%20this%20amazing%20space%20to%20share%20with%20our%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20but%20I%20would%20never%20recommend%20this%20to%20anybody.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224752%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20couple%20sat%20on%20the%20roof%20of%20a%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65412413356802a56be88e0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223168%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESegeren%20wouldn't%20recommend%20a%20project%20like%20this%20to%20anyone.%3Cp%3EClaire%20Segeren%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%