3A%20first%2C%20I%20did%20not%20attempt%20to%20sneak%20any%20products%20or%20otherwise%20trick%20the%20scanner%20into%20not%20ringing%20up%20an%20item%3B%20second%2C%20I%20do%20not%20know%20exactly%20what%20would%20trigger%20an%20alarm%20because%20Walmart%20does%20not%20disclose%20details%20about%20its%20security%20systems%20with%20the%20press.%20(I've%20asked.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20my%20conversations%20with%20shoppers%2C%20I've%20learned%20that%20problems%20tend%20to%20arise%20with%20large%20or%20bulky%20items%2C%20multiple%20items%20of%20the%20same%20kind%2C%20and%20especially%20when%20using%20the%20handheld%20scanner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grabbed%20one%20of%20the%20store's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-shoppers-divided-stores-redesigned-taller-carts-phone-slot-cupholder-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enewly%20redesigned%20shopping%20carts%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20picked%20up%20a%20case%20of%20bottled%20water%2C%20a%20jumbo%20pack%20of%20toilet%20paper%2C%20and%20some%20desk%20supplies%2C%20including%20three%20stenographer%20notebooks%20(I%20still%20take%20notes%20by%20hand).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221593%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20shopping%20cart%20with%20water%20and%20other%20items%20at%20Walmart.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654006190487ff031cb26ea9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222124%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGrabbing%20a%20few%20work-from-home%20supplies%20from%20Walmart.%3Cp%3EDominick%20Reuter%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20four%20self-checkout%20kiosks%20were%20in%20use%2C%20and%20everyone%20appeared%20to%20be%20getting%20through%20without%20any%20issues.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-costco-kroger-facing-self-checkout-reckoning-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwo%20employees%20were%20monitoring%20the%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20one%20within%20the%20che