usinessinsider.com%2Fwalmarts-5-star-checkout-survey-frustrates-customers-employees-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleave%20a%20five-star%20rating%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screen%20at%20a%20Walmart%20self-checkout%20kiosk%20displays%20a%20survey%20asking%20the%20user%20%26quot%3BHow%20satisfied%20are%20you%20with%20your%20visit%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20prompting%20them%20to%20provide%20a%20rating%20from%20one%20to%20five%20stars.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6532e5e796f7540cd0624114%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20satisfaction%20survey%20pops%20up%20at%20checkout.%3Cp%3EDominick%20Reuter%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20way%20outside%2C%20I%20heard%20a%20chime%20that%20I%20thought%20might%20have%20been%20from%20a%20security%20label%20on%20one%20of%20my%20items%2C%20but%20nobody%20approached%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20scan%20that%20the%20kiosk%20%26quot%3Bmissed%26quot%3B%20was%20the%20fourth%20scan%20I%20intentionally%20did%20on%20the%20three%20notebooks%20to%20see%20if%20the%20system%20would%20warn%20me%20of%20the%20mismatched%20quantities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20people%20paying%20for%20things%20and%20not%20taking%20them%20is%20far%20less%20of%20a%20problem%20for%20retailers%20than%20people%20taking%20things%20and%20not%20paying%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it%20would%20seem%20that%20the%20same%20technology%20could%20be%20used%20to%20check%20for%20order%20accuracy%20and%20might%20inspire%20some%20confidence%20in%20these%20systems.%20In%20my%20case%2C%20I%20consider%20the%20extra%20%241.12%20to%20be%20the%20cost%20of%20this%20little%20experiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20Walmart%20visit%2C%20the%20process%20was%20surprisingly%20drama-free.%20But%20I%20know%20many%20customers%20have%20run%20into%20issues.%20And%20I'd%20love%20to%20hear%20your%2