907828474000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1s_pTipXLJJdRrCazNUvmh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0Explanation%20of%20Vote%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0(EoV)%20on%20the%20UNGA%20resolution%20on%20Thursday%20on%20Gaza%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fun-resolution-urging-immediate-gaza-ceasefire-passes-with-overwhelming-majority%2F%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20abstention%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20a%20mistake.%20Our%20diplomacy%20has%20become%20entrapped%20in%20our%20solidarity%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20topmost%20consideration%20for%20India%20at%20the%20UNGA%20debate%20should%20have%20been%20that%20the%20draft%20was%20tabled%20by%20the%20Arab%20and%20Organisation%20of%20Islamic%20Cooperation%20(OIC)%20countries%20with%20whom%20India%20has%20fraternal%20ties%2C%20and%2C%20second%2C%20it%20called%20for%20an%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%2C%20durable%20and%20sustained%20humanitarian%20truce%E2%80%9D%20in%20Gaza%2C%20which%20is%20an%20urgent%20necessity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-refuses-to-back-landslide-un-general-assembly-call-for-humanitarian-truce-in-gaza%5C%22%3EIndia%20Refuses%20to%20Back%20Landslide%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20Call%20for%20Humanitarian%20Truce%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EYet%2C%20France%20outclassed%20us%2C%20exposing%20the%20need%20for%20more%20creative%20UN%20diplomacy%20on%20our%20part.%20France%20not%20only%20sought%20that%20some%20reference%20to%20Hamas%E2%80%99%20raid%20into%20Israel%20on%20October%207%20be%20made%20in%20the%20draft%20but%20on%20a%20recent%20visit%20to%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20even%20proposed%20an%20alliance%20of%20like-minded%20countries%20to%20take%20on%20Hamas%20militarily.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EYet%2C%20when%20it%20came%20to%20the%20crunch%2C%20France%20ultimately%20voted%20for%20the%20Arab%20resolution%20and%20issued%20an%20EoV%20justifying%20it.%20As%20France%20saw%20it%2C%20the%20imperative%20need%20today%20is%20to%20stop%20the%20fighting%20and%20the%20compelling%20reality%20is%20the%20importance%20of%20being%20on%20the%20right%20side%20of%20history%20on%20the%20Middle%20East%20crisis%2C%20where%20it%20has%20high%20stakes.%20In%20the%20final%20analysis%2C%20what%20stands%20out%20for%20the%20record%20is%20the%20actual%20voting%2C%20not%20the%20EoV.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20apparent%20that%20the%20Canadian%20amendment%20%E2%80%93%20at%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20behest%20and%20sponsored%20by%20Washington%20%E2%80%93%20was%20a%20clumsy%20attempt%20to%20divide%20the%20votes%20by%20calling%20for%20%E2%80%9Cunequivocally%20rejecting%20and%20condemning%20the%20terrorist%20attacks%20by%20Hamas.%E2%80%9D%20In%20a%20notable%20speech%20that%20drew%20wide%20acclaim%2C%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20ambassador%20to%20the%20UN%20Munir%20Akram%20highlighted%20the%20contradiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25123525%2FF9O1QYgbQAARmyY.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25123525%2FF9O1QYgbQAARmyY.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25123525%2FF9O1QYgbQAARmyY-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25123525%2FF9O1QYgbQAARmyY-1024x678.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681609%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22794%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGaza.%20Photo%3AX%2F%40MofaPPD%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIf%20Canada%20was%20being%20fair%20in%20its%20amendment%2C%20he%20said%2C%20it%20should%20also%20agree%20to%20name%20Israel%20as%20well%20as%20Hamas.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20all%20know%20who%20started%20this.%20It%20is%2050%20years%20of%20Israeli%20occupation%20and%20the%20killing%20of%20Palestinians%20with%20impunity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Akram%20argued%2C%20therefore%2C%20not%20naming%20either%20side%20was%20the%20best%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20appears%20that%20India%20was%20taken%20aback%20by%20Akram%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20at%20the%20UNGA%20during%20Agenda%20Item%2070%2C%20Right%20to%20Self-Determination%2C%20where%20he%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpakun.org%2Fstatements%2FThird_Committee%2F2023%2F10272023-01.pdf%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fpakun.org%2Fstatements%2FThird_Committee%2F2023%2F10272023-01.pdf%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1698907828474000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3CuZ4XDQnwGSmSCs2nZ9Qg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0forcefully%20linked%20the%20Palestine%20issue%20and%20the%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%20problem.%20Alas%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20abstention%20has%20only%20left%20the%20centre%20stage%20for%20Pakistan%20to%20occupy.%20This%20could%20be%20consequential.%20A%20prudent%20course%20would%20have%20been%20to%20identify%20with%20the%20stance%20of%20the%20Arab%20countries%20unequivocally%2C%20since%20this%20is%20a%20core%20issue%20for%20them%20and%20it%20is%20playing%20out%20in%20their%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIndia%20should%20have%20factored%20in%20that%20feelings%20are%20running%20high%20in%20the%20West%20Asian%20region%20and%20the%20US-Israeli%20propaganda%20that%20the%20Arab%20world%20paid%20only%20lip%20service%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20hold%20good.%20There%20is%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.ahram.org.eg%2FNews%2F511167.aspx%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fenglish.ahram.org.eg%2FNews%2F511167.aspx%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1698907828474000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0L9DYr3RLnilnf-aG46x01%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0unmistakable%20anger%20and%20anguish%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0among%20the%20regional%20states%20and%20a%20groundswell%20of%20opinion%20has%20appeared%20demanding%20a%20settlement%20of%20the%20Palestine%20issue%20for%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-global-south-gaza-israel-sarang-shidore-interview%5C%22%3EIndia%20Says%20It%20Is%20%E2%80%98Leader%E2%80%99%20of%20Global%20South%20But%20UN%E2%80%99s%20Gaza%20Vote%20Shows%20It%20Has%20No%20Followers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20tectonic%20plates%20of%20regional%20politics%20have%20shifted%20following%20the%20Saudi-Iranian%C2%A0rapprochement%C2%A0under%20China%E2%80%99s%20mediation%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20triggered%20new%20thinking%20in%20West%20Asia%20giving%20impetus%20to%20a%20focus%20on%20development.%20Equally%2C%20the%20regional%20states%20prefer%20to%20address%20their%20issues%20increasingly%20on%20their%20own%20steam%2C%20without%20external%20interference.%20China%20and%20Russia%20understand%20this%20but%20the%20US%20refuses%20to%20see%20the%20writing%20on%20the%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20will%20prove%20to%20be%20damaging%20to%20our%20interests%20if%20a%20growing%20perception%20crystallises%20that%20Indians%20are%20carpetbaggers.%20Indo-Israeli%20fusion%20through%20the%20past%20decade%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20gone%20unnoticed%20in%20the%20Muslim%20countries.%20They%20resent%20it%2C%20perhaps%2C%20but%20it%20may%20not%20surge%20into%20view%20because%20Arabs%20are%20a%20hospitable%20people.%20That%20said%2C%20their%20resentment%20may%20surface%20if%20push%20comes%20to%20shove%20and%20their%20core%20in