%20he%20used%20%26quot%3Bderogatory%20language%26quot%3B%20for%20a%20sitting%20judge%2C%20who%20had%20dismissed%20his%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Kait%20also%20imposed%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20on%20the%20contemnor%2C%20Naresh%20Sharma%2C%20and%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20shocked%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20averments%20made%20by%20him%20in%20his%20case%20pending%20before%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20as%20a%20responsible%20citizen%2C%20the%20contemnor%20was%20expected%20to%20set-forth%20his%20grievances%20in%20a%20civilised%20manner%20while%20maintaining%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20court%20and%20judicial%20process%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hereby%20hold%20the%20contemnor%20guilty%20of%20the%20Contempt%20of%20Courts%20Act%2C%201971%20and%20consequently%2C%20we%20sentence%20him%20to%20undergo%20simple%20imprisonment%20for%20a%20period%20of%20six%20months%20with%20fine%20of%20Rs.2%2C000%2F-%20and%20in%20default%20of%20payment%20of%20fine%2C%20he%20shall%20undergo%20simple%20imprisonment%20of%20seven%20days.%20The%20contemnor%20is%20directed%20to%20be%20taken%20into%20custody%20by%20HC%20Vinod%20(Naib%20Court)%2C%20who%20shall%20handover%20his%20custody%20to%20the%20Tihar%20Jail%2C%20Delhi%20today%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20ordered%20the%20bench%2C%20also%20comprising%20Justice%20Shalinder%20Kaur%2C%20in%20an%20order%20passed%20on%20October%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20contempt%20case%20arose%20from%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20contemnor%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Pathankot%20in%20Punjab%2C%20seeking%20immediate%20criminal%20prosecution%20of%20Union%20of%20India%2C%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20Mumbai%20Police%2C%20Bengaluru%20Police%2C%20Sir%20Dorabji%20Tata%20Trust%2C%20Sir%20Ratan%20Tata%20Trust%2C%20Government%20Ministries%2C%20Departments%2C%20etc.%20for%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bextreme%20crimes%26quot%3B%20inflicted%20upon%20him%20and%20the%20people%20of%20India%20at%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20was%20dismissed%20with%20costs%20by%20the%20single%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20contemnor%20then%20filed%20an%20appeal%20before%20a%20division%20bench%20seeking%20death%20penalty%20for%20the%20judge%20for%20her%20%26quot%3Bdefamatory%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bseditious%26quot%3B%20decision%20and%20also%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20seeking%20her%20prosecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20the%20division%20bench%20dealing%20with%20his%20appeal%20issued%20a%20show%20cause%20notice%20to%20him%20asking%20why%20contempt%20proceedings%20be%20not%20initiated%20for%20levelling%20unsubstantiated%2C%20whimsical%20allegations%20against%20a%20high%20court%20judge%20and%20comparing%20her%20to%20a%20devil.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20present%20appeal%20contains%20unsubstantiated%20and%20whimsical%20allegations%20of%20criminal%20acts%20by%20learned%20single%20judge%20seeking%20the%20punishment%20of%20death%20penalty%20and%20a%20comparison%20of%20the%20judge%20to%20the%20devil%2C%20which%20is%20distasteful%20and%20unacceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20passing%20the%20present%20order%20on%20sentence%2C%20the%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20contemnor%20made%20allegations%20not%20against%20a%20sitting%20judge%20but%20that%20the%20%26quot%3BDelhi%20High%20Court%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20is%20involved%20in%20making%20the%20criminal%20situation%20more%20complicated%20by%20committing%20crime%20upon%20crime%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20contemnor%20has%20sought%20criminal%20action%20against%20the%20learned%20single%20judge%20by%20stating%20that%20Article%2014%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20does%20not%20allow%20mixing%20unrelated%20thing%2C%20and%20so%20the%20single%20bench%20should%20be%20criminally%20charged%20with.%20The%20contemnor%20has%20also%20raised%20derogatory%20allegations%20against%20the%20Hon'ble%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20even%20emphasizes%20punishment%20of%20death%20penalty%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20emphasised.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20contemnor%20has%20used%20utter%20derogatory%20language%20for%20the%20learned%20single%20bench%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20saying%20that%20the%20learned%20single%20judge%20is%20a%20'thief%E2%80%9F%20and%20he%20has%20full%20proof%20of%20the%20same%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20added%20that%20during%20the%20proceedings%2C%20the%20contemnor%20stood%20by%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20him%20against%20the%20single%20judge%20as%20well%20as%20the%20officers%20of%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20the%20judiciary%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bhas%20no%20repentance%20for%20his%20conduct%20and%20actions%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20contemnor%20who%20claims%20to%20have%20been%20educated%20in%20engineering%20and%20science%20from%20one%20of%20the%20most%20reputed%20educational%20institutions%20of%20India%20i.e.%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20Bombay%20and%20in%20USA%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20respect%20the%20Constitutionality%20of%20India%20and%20have%20faith%20in%20the%20legal%20system%20of%20law.%20As%20a%20responsible%20citizen%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20contemnor%20is%20expected%20to%20set-forth%20his%20grievances%20in%20a%20civilised%20manner%2C%20maintaining%20the%20dignity%20of%20the%20court%20and%20judicial%20process%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698829380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-09%2Fjudge-court-generic-istock_650x400_81473483517.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-goes-to-court-seeking-judges-death-penalty-sent-to-jail-for-6-months-4534220%2