ia%20Zwicker%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20family%20has%20an%20overall%20goal%20of%20lowering%20our%20footprint%20and%20getting%20off%20all%20fossil%20fuels.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20a%20little%20while%20to%20be%20ready%20financially%2C%20and%20we%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20research%20before%20making%20the%20choice.%20In%20August%202020%2C%20we%20started%20a%20lease%20on%20a%202020%20Chevrolet%20Bolt.%20Two%20months%20later%2C%20we%20bought%20a%20second%2C%20used%20Bolt.%20Both%20have%20about%20259%20miles%20of%20range.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20reason%20for%20the%20Bolt%20was%20it%20was%20the%20most%20affordable%20option.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-electric-car-lease-vs-purchase-buying-tips-cost-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20I%20chose%20to%20lease%20because%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20figured%20the%20EV%20landscape%20would%20change%20a%20lot%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20lease%2C%20and%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20that%20was%20the%20best%20financial%20decision.%20I%20ended%20up%20buying%20out%20the%20lease%2C%20too.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bolt%20is%20the%20slowest%20of%20fast-charging%20cars%2C%20and%20that's%20the%20biggest%20downside%20to%20it.%20What%20I%20didn't%20expect%20is%20a%20kind%20of%20pooh-poohing%20at%20Bolt%20drivers%20specifically%2C%20because%20our%20cars%20charge%20slowly.%20Other%20EV%20drivers%20get%20upset%20at%20us%20taking%20up%20time%20at%20charging%20stations.%20The%20next%20EV%20for%20us%20will%20be%20something%20that%20can%20charge%20faster.%20We've%20got%20our%20eye%20on%20the%20Equinox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20only%20have%20Level-1%20charging%20at%20home%2C%20because%20we%20just%20don't%20need%20anything%20else.%20My%20husband%20has%20free%20Level-2%20charging%20at%20work%2C%20and%20I%20also%20had%20that%20for%20some%20time.%20We%20public%20charge%20when%20we%20road%20trip%2C%20so%20that's%20the%20most%20we%20ever%20pay.%20Just%20something%20I've%20become%20used%20to%20is%3A%20Always%20have%20a%20backup%20plan.%20Make%20sure%20you%20understand%20how%20fast%20charging%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBob%20McGill%2C%2078%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0League%20City%2C%20TX%20%E2%80%94%20Tesla%20Model%203%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20his%20Tesla%20in%20a%20driveway.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653fe0a296f7540cd06965b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBob%20McGill%20drives%20a%20Tesla.%3Cp%3EBob%20McGill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20August%202022%2C%20I%20took%20delivery%20of%20a%20new%20Tesla%20Model%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20been%20thinking%20about%20it%20for%20a%20while%20for%20all%20the%20usual%20things%2C%20like%20not%20having%20to%20buy%20gas%2C%20and%20I'm%20a%20retired%20computer%20nerd%20so%20I%20like%20cutting-edge%20technology.%20I%20considered%20the%20Nissan%20Leaf%20for%20a%20while%20and%20the%20Chevrolet%20Bolt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20primarily%20charge%20at%20home%20and%20rarely%20charge%20outside%20the%20house.%20I%20bought%20the%20home%20charging%20unit%20from%20Tesla%2C%20and%20an%20electrician%20friend%20installed%20it%20for%20me.%20It%20costs%20about%20%2450%20per%20month%20for%20electricity.%20I%20don't%20plug%20it%20in%20every%20night.%20I%20get%20about%20300%20miles%20on%20a%20charge%20and%20I%20have%20over%2022%2C000%20miles%20on%20the%20car%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20not%20having%20to%20do%20any%20maintenance.%20There's%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20learning%20curve%20about%20charging.%20There%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20anxiety%20at%20first%20about%20being%20able%20to%20charge%20whenever%20I%20needed%20to.%20But%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20there's%20plenty%20around.%20It's%20not%20difficult%20to%20do%20that.%20I%20took%20a%20trip%20to%20Alabama%20in%20May%2C%20and%20I've%20never%20driven%20the%20Tesla%20over%20there%2C%20but%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20places%20to%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20somebody%20feels%20like%20EV%20is%20what%20they%20want%20to%20do%2C%20they%20should.%20They're%20a%20little%20more%20expensive%2C%20but%20the%20amount%20of%20gas%20savings%20will%20make%20up%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELisa%20Holland%2C%2059%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Atlanta%2C%20GA%20%E2%80%94%20Ford%20Mustang%20Mach-E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222663%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20her%20silver%20SUV%20in%20front%20of%20a%20lake%20with%20green%20trees.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653fdf8e0487ff031cb2263b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223551%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELisa%20Holland%20owns%20a%20Mustang%20Mach-E.%3Cp%3ELisa%20Holland%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20wanted%20a%20Leaf%20when%20it%20came%20out%2C%20but%20the%20range%20wasn't%20very%20practical%20because%20we%20do%20go%20to%20Florida%20a%20lot.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-model-3-model-y-less-than-average-gas-car-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETeslas%20became%20more%20affordable%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20with%20more%20range%2C%20and%20I%20toyed%20with%20that.%20I%20was%20driving%20an%20SUV%20at%20the%20time%20and%20it%20was%20costing%20too%20much%20to%20fill%20up%2C%20so%20that's%20when%20I%20started%20looking%20hard%20for%20an%20EV.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20my%20Mustang%20in%202021%2C%20the%20California%20Route%201%20trim%20for%20about%20%2445%2C000%20with%20the%20%247%2C500%20tax%20credit.%20There%20was%20absolutely%20no%20maintenance%2C%20no%20oil%20changes%2C%20no%20transmission%20problems%C2%A0%E2%80%94%C2%A0just%20a%20car%20sitting%20on%20a%20battery.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20charge%20at%20home%20at%20night%2C%20my%20utility%20gives%20me%20a%20discounted%20rate%20to%20charge%20off-peak%20hours%2C%20so%20my%20power%20bill%20has%20only%20gone%20up%20%2413%20at%20most.%20They%20also%20gave%20me%20a%20rebate%20when%20I%20had%20an%20electrician%20put%20the%20outlet%20in%20my%20garage.%20Ford%20provided%20the%20charger.%20Last%20December%2C%20I%20traded%20in%20the%20first%20Mustang%20for%20the%20GT.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20I%20was%20concerned%20about%20most%20was%20range%20and%20getting%20out%20of%20state.%20Traveling%20is%20a%20little%20difficult%20for%20me%20here%20in%20the%20Southeast%2C%20especially%20going%20to%20the%20Panhandle%20in%20Florida.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20that%20I%20talk%20to%20are%20concerned%20about%20batteries%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20replacing%20them.%20I%20think%20that's%20a%20big%20misconception.%20It's%20just%20been%20great%20for%20me%2C%20because%20I'm%20saving%20so%20much%20money%2C%20not%20spending%20it%20on%20gas%20or%20maintenance.%20It's%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJason%20Luu%2C%2031%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Los%20Angeles%2C%20CA%20%E2%80%94%20Tesla%20Model%203%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20black%20Tesla%20parked%20in%20a%20lot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653fe10a96f7540cd069662d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJason%20Luu%20drives%20this%20Tesla.%3Cp%3EJason%20Luu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20my%20Tesla%20Model%203%20in%202019.%20One%20of%20the%20biggest%20reasons%20why%20I%20got%20it%20was%20to%20not%20have%20to%20go%20to%20the%20pump%20anymore.%20I%20like%20tech-savvy%20things%2C%20and%20so%20I%20thought%20I'd%20get%20ahead%20of%20that%20curve.%20Another%20selling%20point%20for%20me%20were%20the%20tax%20incentives%20at%20the%20time.%20I%20did%20get%20the%20%247%2C500%20federal%20tax%20incentive%2C%20and%20the%20state%20of%20California%20also%20offered%20%242%2C000.%20My%20utility%20provider%20also%20offered%20another%20%241%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20installed%20a%20220-volt%20outlet%20in%20my%20home%20and%20I've%20done%20that%20in%20my%20new%20home%20as%20well.%20I%20know%20that%20that%20might%20be%20a%20deterrent%20for%20some.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20very%20densely%20populated%20city%20like%20LA%2C%20for%20those%20living%20in%20like%20either%20condominium%20buildings%20or%20apartment%20buildings%2C%20they%20might%20not%20have%20that%20kind%20of%20infrastructure%20to%20charge%20overnight.%20But%20then%20I've%20been%20pretty%20impressed%20with%20the%20Supercharger%20network.%20Luckily%2C%20my%20work%20has%20charging%20stations%20where%20I%20can%20charge%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20like%20when%20people%20think%20about%20purchasing%20EVs%2C%20they%20get%20a%20little%20hesitant%20on%20range%20anxiety.%20But%20on%20a%20given%20day%2C%20the%20average%20person%20is%20not%20going%20more%20than%20the%20full%20capacity%20of%20the%20battery%2C%20and%20you%20wake%20up%20and%20have%20a%20full%20charge.%20From%20a%20charge%20perspective%2C%20having%20it%20installed%20at%20your%20home%20and%20having%20that%20capability%20really%20is%20a%20game%20changer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20the%20average%20person%2C%20you%20map%20out%20your%20day.%20There's%20not%20much%20uncertainty%20in%20terms%20of%20where%20you're%20going.%20You're%20going%20to%20work%2C%20home%2C%20and%20stopping%20by%20the%20grocery%20store.%20You%20can%20plan%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJerry%20Schotz%2C%2059%20%E2%80%94%20Champaign-Urbana%2C%20IL%20%E2%80%94%20Chevrolet%20Bolt%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20white%20car%20and%20a%20red%20car%20parked%20side-by-side.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653fe0e1356802a56be792c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJerry%20Schotz%20has%20two%20Chevrolet%20Bolts.%3Cp%3EJerry%20Schotz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20two%20gas-powered%20cars.%20In%20May%202021%2C%20I%20purchased%20my%20first%20EV%2C%20a%20new%202021%20Chevrolet%20Bolt.%20When%20we%20tried%20the%20EV%2C%20we%20were%20a%20little%20leery%20of%20what%20it%20was%20going%20to%20be%20like%2C%20so%20I%20still%20kept%20my%20Toyota%20RAV4.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202021%2C%20we%20found%20a%20used%202020%20Chevrolet%20Bolt%2C%20trading%20in%20my%20wife's%202017%20Nissan%20Altima%20for%20it.%20We%20were%20fully%20electric%20by%20the%20beginning%20of%202022.%20We're%20surprised%20a%20little%20bit%20at%20the%20vitriol%20that%20we%20get%20from%20people%20because%20we%20own%20EVs%2C%20but%20we've%20been%20very%20happy%20with%20it%20since%20then.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20batteries%20have%20been%20replaced%20during%20the%20recall.%20The%20only%20maintenance%20has%20been%20tire%20rotations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20put%20a%20220-volt%20outlet%20in%20the%20garage%20and%20plug%20in%20the%20car%20there%2C%20since%2090%25%20of%20our%20travel%20is%20local.%20Between%20the%20electrical%20panel%20upgrade%20and%20the%20outlet%2C%20it%20was%20around%20%241%2C500.%20This%20year%20is%20also%20our%20first%20year%20having%20our%20own%20solar%20on%20the%20house%2C%20so%20now%20we're%20driving%20completely%20for%20free.%20Before%20we%20did%20solar%2C%20it%20was%20probably%20adding%20%2450%20a%20month%20to%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20took%20our%20first%20road%20trip%20to%20Branson%2C%20Missouri%2C%20from%20Central%20Illinois%2C%20a%20good%20eight-hour%20drive%2C%20and%20I%20plotted%20out%20the%20routes%20with%20planners%20and%20PlugShare.%20It%20was%20a%20little%20hard%20to%20find%20fast-charging%20but%20we%20made%20it%20there%20and%20back%20without%20any%20problems.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20took%20a%20trip%20to%20Wisconsin%2C%20we've%20taken%20trips%20to%20Indiana%2C%20through%20Tennessee%2C%20and%20Kentucky.%20Electrify%20America%20saves%20us%20pretty%20much%20all%20the%20time.%20I%20think%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20things%20about%20charging%20that%20was%20surprising%20to%20me%20is%20how%20slow%20even%20fast%20charging%20gets%20in%20the%20wintertime%2C%20because%20of%20all%20the%20protections%20for%20the%20battery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegenerative%20braking%20is%20the%20coolest%20thing%20to%20me.%20We're%20happy%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20emissions%20coming%20out%20of%20our%20car.%20We're%20not%20contributing%20to%20any%20sort%20of%20greenhouse%20gases%20from%20driving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-vehicle-owners-advice-realities-cost-maintenance-driving-electric-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698829201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6536d63196f7540cd0636451%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-vehicle-owners-advice-realities-cost-maintenance-driving-electric-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20Californians%20to%20East%20Coasters%2C%20from%20Tesla%20drivers%20to%20Ford%20owners%2C%20here's%20what%20eight%20EV%20fans%20told%20us%20about%20owning%20electric.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22astjohn%40insider.com%20(Alexa%20St.%20John)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-vehicle-owners-advice-realities-cost-maintenance-driving-electric-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20deadline%20to%20leave%20Pakistan%20expires%2C%20official%20says%20over%20100%2C000%20Afghans%20gone%20home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698828443000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104884338%2Cimgsize-1440826.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fas-deadline-to-leave-pakistan-expires-official-says-over-100000-afghans-gone-home%2Farticleshow%2F104884215.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindi