%20virtual%20mode.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESmita%20Pant%2C%20Indian%20MEA%20Joint%20Secretary%20(Bangladesh%20and%20Myanmar)%20said%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ffreight-train-trial-conducted-in-agartala-akhaura-rail-route%2Farticle67308604.ece%2Famp%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20route%20would%20be%20the%20sixth%20operational%20rail%20link%20with%20Bangladesh%20and%20preparations%20are%20on%20to%20establish%20the%20seventh%20with%20Assam.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20the%20successful%20trial%20last%20Thursday%2C%20several%20trials%20took%20place%20in%20the%20last%20few%20weeks.%20The%20project%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20June%202023%20but%20it%20got%20delayed%20due%20to%20construction-related%20issues%2C%20according%20to%20the%20railway%20officials.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETripura%20shares%20an%20856%20km-long%20international%20border%20with%20Bangladesh%2C%20much%20of%20which%20is%20disputed%20locally.%20The%20northeastern%20states%2C%20including%20Tripura%2C%20are%20only%20accessible%20through%20a%20narrow%20strip%20of%20land%20in%20West%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20completion%20of%20this%20railway%20project%2C%20it%20is%20estimated%20that%20the%20travel%20time%20between%20Kolkata%20and%20Tripura%20via%20Dhaka%20will%20be%20reduced%20to%2010%20hours%20from%2031%20hours.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698827681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01140317%2FScreenshot-2023-11-01-at-2.03.12%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fagartala-akhaura-international-rail-link-to-be-inaugurated-soon-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20completion%20of%20this%20railway%20project%2C%20it%20is%20estimated%20that%20the%20travel%20time%20between%20Kolkata%20and%20Tripura%20via%20Dhaka%20will%20be%20reduced%20significantly%2C%20'The%20Hindu'%20has%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fagartala-akhaura-international-rail-link-to-be-inaugurated-soon-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Movies-series%20to%20watch%20on%20Netflix%20in%20November%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698827560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104883426%2Cimgsize-74332.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fmovies-and-series-to-enjoy-on-netflix-in-november%2Fphotostory%2F104883426.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104883426.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMovies%20and%20series%20to%20enjoy%20on%20Netflix%20in%20November%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Fmovies-and-series-to-enjoy-on-netflix-in-november%2Fphotostory%2F104883426.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Man%20Dies%2040%20Days%20After%20Receiving%20World's%20Second%20Pig%20Heart%20Transplant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20person%20to%20receive%20a%20transplanted%20heart%20from%20a%20pig%20has%20died%2C%2040%20days%20after%20the%20highly%20experimental%20surgery%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Flawrence-faucette-second-pig-heart-transplant-dies%2Findex.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DLawrence%2520Faucette%252C%2520the%2520second%2520living%2Cof%2520rejection%2520in%2520recent%2520days.%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0Lawrence%20Faucette%2C%2058%2C%20was%20dying%20from%20heart%20failure%20when%20he%20received%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medschool.umaryland.edu%2Fnews%2F2023%2Fum-medicine-faculty-scientists-and-clinicians-perform-second-historic-transplant-of-pig-heart-into-patient-with-end-stage-cardiovascular-disease.html%5C%22%3Egenetically%20modified%20pig%20heart%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20September%2020.%C2%A0According%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland%20School%20of%20Medicine%2C%20the%20heart%20had%20seemed%20healthy%20for%20the%20first%20month%20but%20began%20showing%20signs%20of%20rejection%20in%20recent%20days.%20He%20lived%20for%20nearly%20six%20weeks%20after%20the%20surgery%20and%20died%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E''Mr.%20Faucette%20had%20made%20significant%20progress%20after%20his%20surgery%2C%20engaging%20in%20physical%20therapy%2C%20spending%20time%20with%20family%20members%2C%20and%20playing%20cards%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Ann.%20In%20recent%20days%2C%20his%20heart%20began%20to%20show%20initial%20signs%20of%20rejection%20--the%20most%20significant%20challenge%20with%20traditional%20transplants%20involving%20human%20organs%20as%20well.%20Despite%20the%20medical%20team's%20greatest%20efforts%2C%20Mr.%20Faucette%20ultimately%20succumbed%20on%20October%2030%2C''%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medschool.umaryland.edu%2Fnews%2F2023%2Fin-memoriam-lawrence-faucette.html%5C%22%3Ea%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20hospital%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr.%20Faucette%20was%20a%20Navy%20veteran%20and%20retired%20lab%20technician%20at%20the%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health.%20He%20had%20been%20turned%20down%20for%20a%20traditional%20heart%20transplant%20because%20of%20other%20health%20problems%20when%20he%20came%20to%20the%20Maryland%20hospital.%C2%A0%20Without%20the%20experimental%20transplant%2C%20the%20father%20of%20two%20was%20facing%20near-certain%20heart%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Faucette's%20wife%2C%20Ann%2C%20said%20her%20husband%20''knew%20his%20time%20with%20us%20was%20short%20and%20this%20was%20his%20last%20chance%20to%20do%20for%20others.%20He%20never%20imagined%20he%20would%20survive%20as%20long%20as%20he%20did.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E''Mr.%20Faucette's%20last%20wish%20was%20for%20us%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20what%20we%20have%20learned%20from%20our%20experience%2C%20so%20others%20may%20be%20guaranteed%20a%20chance%20for%20a%20new%20heart%20when%20a%20human%20organ%20is%20unavailable.%20He%20then%20told%20the%20team%20of%20doctors%20and%20nurses%20who%20gathered%20around%20him%20that%20he%20loved%20us.%20We%20will%20miss%20him%20tremendously%2C''%20Dr.%20Bartley%20Griffith%2C%20clinical%20director%20of%20the%20Cardiac%20Xenotransplantation%20Program%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland%20School%20of%20Medicine%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETransplanting%20animal%20organs%20into%20humans%2C%20called%20xenotransplantation%2C%20could%20offer%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20chronic%20shortage%20of%20human%20organ%20donations.%20However%2C%20these%20procedures%20are%20challenging%20because%20the%20patient's%20immune%20system%20attacks%20the%20foreign%20organ.%C2%A0Scientists%20hoped%20that%20genetically%20modifying%20pig%20parts%20to%20make%20them%20more%20like%20human%20organs%20would%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Maryland%20team%20last%20year%20had%20also%20performed%20the%20world's%20first%20transplant%20of%20a%20heart%20from%20a%20genetically%20altered%20pig%20into%20another%20man.%20He%20died%20two%20months%20after%20his%20transplant.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffirst-person-david-bennett-to-receive-pig-heart-transplant-dies-after-2-months-2813517%5C%22%3EDavid%20Bennett%2C%2057%2C%20received%20his%20transplant%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20January%207%2C%202022%2C%20and%20died%20on%20March%208%2C%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland%20Medical%20System%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698827460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22htt