c-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fpakistan-cricket-board-issuing-removal-warnings-to-captain-babar-azam-downgrading-morale-ex-pakistan-star-4530699%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Must%20Apologise%20for%20the%201984%20Sikh%20Pogrom%2C%20With%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Leading%20the%20Charge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01134213%2F3828685307_6cdc23ac11_k.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%2039th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20tragic%201984%20anti-Sikh%20pogrom%20in%20Delhi%2C%20it%20becomes%20imperative%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20magnitude%20of%20violence%20and%20the%20lasting%20shame%20it%20has%20brought.%20Beyond%20political%20manoeuvring%2C%20it%20is%20incumbent%20upon%20the%20Congress%20to%20sincerely%20apologise%20for%20their%20involvement%20in%20the%20unrest.%20In%20his%20emerging%20role%20as%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20leader%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20with%20his%20pledge%20to%20foster%20love%20in%20a%20realm%20rife%20with%20hatred%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3ENafrat%20ke%20bazaar%20me%20mohhabbat%20ki%20dukaan%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0should%20take%20the%20lead%20in%20initiating%20the%20process%20of%20reconciliation%20and%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%201984%20Sikh%20massacre%20not%20only%20resulted%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20life%20but%20also%20dealt%20a%20devastating%20blow%20to%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20dignity%20and%20pride.%20Echoing%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20Nanavati%20Commission%20report%2C%20the%20riots%20not%20only%20inflicted%20pain%20on%20the%20Sikh%20populace%20but%20also%20jolted%20the%20conscience%20of%20all%20right-thinking%20individuals%20across%20the%20nation.%20The%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20investigations%20into%20the%20cases%20in%20Delhi%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20such%20as%20Bokaro%20and%20Kanpur%2C%20unearthed%20not%20just%20mass%20killings%20but%20also%20the%20active%20participation%20of%20Congress%20workers%20and%20certain%20%E2%80%98prominent%E2%80%99%20leaders%20of%20this%20party.%20Despite%20affording%20these%20leaders%20the%20opportunity%20to%20defend%20themselves%2C%20they%20failed%20to%20provide%20a%20compelling%20defence%20and%20instead%20resorted%20to%20manipulating%20facts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENearly%20four%20decades%20have%20passed%20since%20those%20tragic%20events%20unfolded.%20While%20some%20advocate%20for%20the%20Sikh%20community%20to%20move%20on%20and%20introspect%2C%20it%20is%20unjust%20to%20sweep%20their%20anguish%20and%20trauma%20under%20the%20rug.%20Numerous%20reports%2C%20including%20those%20by%20the%20Nanavati%20Commission%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdelhi-hc-1984-massacres-a-crime-against-humanity-india-must-plug-legal-loopholes%5C%22%3E2018%20verdict%20by%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20indicate%20that%20Sikhs%20have%20been%20hesitant%20to%20share%20their%20narratives%20with%20the%20world%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20sense%20of%20isolation%20and%20alienation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20adage%20%E2%80%9Cjustice%20delayed%20is%20justice%20denied%E2%80%9D%20rings%20true.%20The%20Sikh%20community%20has%20been%20losing%20faith%20in%20the%20judicial%20system%2C%20and%20this%20feeling%20of%20alienation%20is%20deeply%20ingrained%20in%20their%20lived%20experiences.%20While%20Justice%20S.%20Muralidhar%20displayed%20sensitivity%20and%20humility%20in%20acknowledging%20the%20pain%2C%20suffering%20and%20trauma%20endured%20by%20the%20Sikh%20community%2C%20his%20sentencing%20of%20culprits%20such%20as%20Sajjan%20Kumar%20and%20various%20Congress%20workers%20begs%20the%20larger%20question%20%E2%80%93%20can%20it%20truly%20be%20considered%20justice%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Review%3A%20India%20in%201984%2C%20and%20a%20World%20Bound%20By%20Compassion%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fradhika-oberoi-stillborn-season%5C%22%3EIndia%20in%201984%2C%20and%20a%20World%20Bound%20By%20Compassion%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20primary%20issues%20at%20hand%20is%20the%20refusal%20of%20the%20perpetrators%20to%20accept%20responsibility%20for%20their%20actions.%20Leaders%20such%20as%20Kamal%20Nath%20and%20Jagdish%20Tytler%20are%20yet%20to%20apologise%20or%20even%20admit%20their%20involvement%2C%20despite%20eyewitness%20accounts%20presented%20in%20court.%20Disturbingly%2C%20not%20only%20have%20these%20culprits%E2%80%99%20evaded%20justice%2C%20but%20they%20have%20also%20been%20rewarded%20with%20high%20political%20positions%2C%20including%20roles%20as%20MLAs%2C%20MPs%2C%20ministers%20and%20even%20chief%20minister.%20Even%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZb01XTXPfLg%5C%22%3Eadmitted%20in%20a%20television%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20certain%20Congress%20leaders%20were%20complicit%20in%20the%20tragic%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Nanavati%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20to%20the%20conscience%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20the%20liberal%20section%20of%20Indian%20society%20has%20failed%20to%20recognise%20the%20Sikh%20community%20as%20victims.%20The%20term%20%E2%80%98riots%E2%80%99%20itself%20is%20a%20bone%20of%20contention%20for%20Sikhs%2C%20as%20it%20implies%20clashes%20between%20two%20sides%2C%20whereas%20the%20events%20of%201984%20constituted%20targeted%20violence%2C%20akin%20to%20genocide%2C%20with%20Sikhs%20as%20the%20sole%20victims.%20While%20the%20liberal%20section%20raises%20concerns%20over%20the%20rehabilitation%20of%20rapists%20and%20the%20welcoming%20of%20accused%20individuals%2C%20they%20often%20fail%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20Congress%20leaders%20who%20have%20either%20been%20convicted%20or%20faced%20serious%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20response%20to%20queries%20about%20the%201984%20tragedy%20has%20been%20problematic.%20During%20his%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20he%20evaded%20condemning%20the%20events%20directly%2C%20instead%20referencing%20statements%20made%20by%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20and%20former%20Congress%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%20His%20reluctance%20to%20apologise%20is%20disheartening%2C%20given%20his%20vocal%20pride%20in%20the%20achievements%20of%20his%20family%20members%2C%20such%20as%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20Rajiv%20Gandhi.%20If%20one%20takes%20pride%20in%20their%20virtues%2C%20one%20must%20acknowledge%20their%20vices%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20recent%20visit%20to%20Darbar%20Sahib%2C%20Amritsar%2C%20and%20his%20acts%20of%20%3Cem%3ESewa%3C%2Fem%3E%20during%20ordinary%20days%20of%20the%20Nanakshahi%20calendar%20may%20have%20been%20interpreted%20as%20a%20significant%20gesture%2C%20it%20remains%20imperative%20to%20question%20the%20concrete%20actions%20taken%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20Gandhi%20towards%20reconciliation%20and%20the%20wellbeing%20of%20the%20families%20affected%20by%20the%201984%20tragedy.%20Nowadays%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20visiting%20various%20sections%20of%20society%20and%20sharing%20videos%20of%20his%20visits%20on%20social%20media.%20Can%20he%20pay%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20widow%20colony%20of%20Tilak%20Nagar%20in%20Delhi%2C%20where%20many%20men%20fell%20victim%20to%20the%20horrific%20events%20of%20November%201984%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22If%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20Asked%20About%20the%201984%20Killings%20Again%2C%20This%20is%20What%20He%20Should%20Say%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frahul-gandhi-congress-party-1984-riots%5C%22%3EIf%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20Asked%20About%20the%201984%20Killings%20Again%2C%20This%20is%20What%20He%20Should%20Say%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Frahul-gandhi-caste-census-obc-women-reservation-8951130%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHe%2520said%253A%2520%25E2%2580%259C100%2520per%2520cent%2Cthat%2520did%2520the%2520caste%2520census.%5C%22%3Erecent%20expression%20of%20regret%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20failure%20to%20conduct%20a%20caste%20census%20and%20implement%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservations%20is%20commendable.%20Shouldn%E2%80%99t%20the%20same%20regret%20be%20extended%20to%20the%20Sikh%20community%3F%20While%20these%20families%20require%20special%20social%20security%20measures%20and%20an%20environment%20conducive%20to%20their%20well-being%2C%20what%20Sikhs%20truly%20seek%20is%20a%20straightforward%20admission%20and%20apology%20from%20Gandhi%2C%20should%20he%20wish%20to%20be%20their%20leader.%20This%20sentiment%20resonates%20across%20the%20global%20Punjabi%20community.%20Rehabilitation%2C%20psychological%20support%20and%20community%20engagement%20can%20follow%2C%20but%20the%20initial%20acknowledgment%20of%20wrongdoing%20is%20a%20necessary%20step%20toward%20reconciliation%20and%20the%20restoration%20of%20respect%20for%20the%20Sikh%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENo%20matter%20how%20many%20visits%20Gandhi%20makes%20to%20the%20gurudwaras%2C%20his%20trust%20among%20Sikhs%20and%20Punjabis%20will%20remain%20elusive%20unless%20he%20acknowledges%20past%20grievances%20and%20initiates%20dialogue%20for%20reconciliation.%20If%20he%20truly%20espouses%20the%20ethos%20of%20Sikhi%2C%20he%20must%20embody%20the%20principle%20of%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Mann%20niwan%2C%20matt%20uchi%20(%3C%2Fem%3Ebeing%20humble%20in%20mind%20and%20elevated%20in%20thinking)%E2%80%99%20and%20earnestly%20extend%20his%20goodwill%20towards%20the%20Sikh%20community.%20Electoral%20manoeuvring%20notwithstanding%2C%20the%20pressing%20reality%20is%20that%20Sikhs%20require%20a%20compassionate%20leader%20who%20is%20willing%20to%20lend%20an%20ear%2C%20facilitate%20healing%20and%20foster%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHarinder%20Happy%20is%20a%20PhD%20Scholar%20at%20the%20Centre%20of%20Social%20Medicine%20and%20Community%20Health%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharinderhappy.jnu%40gmail.com%5C%22%3Eharinderhappy.jnu%40gmail.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698827451000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01134213%2F3828685307_6cdc23ac11_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fcongress-must-apologise-for-the-1984-sikh-pogrom-will-rahul-gandhi-leading-the-charge%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rehabilitation%2C%20psychological%20support%20and%20community%20engagement%20can%20follow%2C%20but%20the%20initial%20acknowledgment%20of%20wrongdoing%20is%20a%20necessary%20step%20toward%20reconciliation%20and%20the%20restoration%20of%20respect%20for%20the%20Sikh%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fcongress-must-apologise-for-the-1984-sikh-pogrom-will-rahul-gandhi-leading-the-charge%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20the%20World%20Watches%2C%20Gaza%20Has%20Become%20a%20Graveyard%20for%20Children%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01125649%2FUNI448902.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2030%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Palestine%20Chronicle%3C%2Fem%3E%20ran%20a%20news%20report%20headlined%2C%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.palestinechronicle.com%2Fthe-sweet-boy-with-curly-hair-was-found-but-under-the-rubble%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CAfter%2520the%2520arrival%2520of%2520the%2CHospital%2520in%2520Khan%2520Yunis%2520city.%25E2%2580%259D%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Sweet%20Boy%20with%20Curly%20Hair%E2%80%99%20was%20Found%2C%20but%20Under%20the%20Rubble%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ceiling%20collapsed%20on%20little%20Yusuf%20Musa%20as%20his%20house%20in%20a%20south%20Gaza%20neighbourhood%20was%20hit%20directly%20by%20an%20Israeli%20missile.%20It%20was%20Yusuf%E2%80%99s%20father%20who%20identified%20his%20dead%20son%20in%20the%20hospital%20where%20he%20works%20as%20a%20doctor%20(he%20has%20not%20gone%20home%20in%20the%20last%20three%20weeks)%3B%20the%20hospital%20authorities%20felt%20it%20would%20be%20better%20if%20Yusuf%E2%80%99s%20mother%20did%20not%20see%20her%20son%E2%80%99s%20disfigured%20remains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYusuf%E2%80%99s%20last%20words%20to%20his%20mother%20had%20not%20been%20heavy%20with%20the%20import%20of%20a%20final%20farewell%3B%20on%20the%20contrary%2C%20they%20glimmered%20with%20the%20easy%20certainty%20of%20a%20familiar%20routine%20embellished%20with%20love.%20%E2%80%9CMom%2C%20we%20%5Bhe%20and%20his%20brother%5D%20want%20to%20have%20dinner%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20is%20what%20he%20said%20when%20his%20life%20took%20a%20different%20turn%2C%20towards%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGaza%20has%20become%20a%20graveyard%20of%20children%2C%20UN%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Fund%20(UNICEF)%20spokesman%20James%20Elder%20stated%20during%20a%20news%20briefing%20in%20Geneva%20on%20October%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20an%20unspeakable%20situation%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EOn%20October%2031%2C%20the%20Gaza%20health%20ministry%20issued%20a%20statement%20that%20of%20the%208%2C525%20Palestinians%20killed%20in%20the%20past%20three%20weeks%2C%202%2C187%20were%20women%20and%203%2C542%20were%20children.%20That%20means%2041%25%20of%20those%20killed%20so%20far%20have%20been%20children.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EOver%206%2C000%20children%20have%20been%20injured%20and%20about%20900%20children%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20under%20the%20rubble.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EIsraeli%20air%20strikes%20have%20killed%20over%20100%20children%20in%20Gaza%20every%20day%20since%20October%207.%20(In%20the%20first%20six%20days%20alone%2C%20Israel%20dropped%206%2C000%20bombs%20in%20Gaza%2C%20almost%20equalling%20the%20number%20of%20bombs%20dropped%20by%20the%20US%20in%20Afghanistan%20in%20one%20year.)%20UNICEF%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fapple-india-state-sponsored-spyware%5C%22%3Eputs%20the%20figure%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20children%20killed%20and%20injured%20daily%20at%20over%20400.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.savethechildren.net%2Fwhat-we-do%2Femergencies%2Fgaza-emergency%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20Save%20the%20Children%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20number%20of%20casualties%20among%20children%20in%20Gaza%20in%20three%20weeks%20%E2%80%9Csurpasses%20the%20annual%20number%20of%20children%20killed%20across%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20conflict%20zones%20since%202019%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EAnaesthesia%20shortages%20have%20meant%20that%20doctors%20have%20had%20to%20carry%20out%20amputations%20on%20children%20without%20pain%20relief%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHwZ0l2lzjJg%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Doctors%20Without%20Borders%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20complications%20caused%20by%20dehydration%20%E2%80%93%20as%20Gaza%20now%20has%20access%20to%20a%20mere%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fwho-warns-imminent-public-health-catastrophe-gaza-2023-10-31%2F%5C%22%3E5%25%20of%20its%20water%20requirements%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20puts%20the%20lives%20of%20infants%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EChildren%20under%2018%20comprise%20half%20the%20population%20of%202.3%20million%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20end%20to%20the%20images%20of%20grief%20that%20are%20being%20captured%2024%2F7.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMSF%2Fstatus%2F1719444615319691585%5C%22%3EChildren%20by%20themselves%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20hospitals%20after%20air%20strikes%2C%20separated%20from%20their%20families.%20Men%20collecting%20the%20bodies%20of%20their%20children%20wrapped%20in%20bloodstained%20white%20hospital%20sheets%2C%20cradling%20them%20in%20their%20arms%20or%20holding%20them%20aloft%2C%20trying%20to%20shield%20the%20women%20from%20such%20unimaginable%20sights.%20The%20furrows%20on%20their%20faces%20indicating%20that%20the%20grief%2C%20like%20a%20thorn%20embedded%20deep%20in%20the%20flesh%2C%20is%20here%20to%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22On%20the%20Mothers%20of%20Gaza%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fon-the-mothers-of-gaza%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20Mothers%20of%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20deaths%20are%20not%20collateral%2C%20caused%20by%20strikes%20intended%20for%20another%20target%20but%20landing%20on%20people%E2%80%99s%20houses.%20The%20strikes%20are%20deliberate%2C%20as%20the%20intensive%20targeting%20of%20residential%20neighbourhoods%2C%20schools%20and%20hospitals%20indicates.%20The%20Israeli%20intent%20of%20collective%20punishment%20has%20been%20made%20clear%20by%20its%20actions%20of%20cutting%20off%20water%2C%20power%2C%20fuel%20and%20food%2C%20followed%20by%20pulverising%20airstrikes%20and%20now%20a%20ground%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2019%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%20carried%20a%20graphic%20showing%20that%20a%20child%20who%20was%20two%20years%20of%20age%20in%202008%20has%20lived%20through%20five%20crushing%20Israeli%20wars%3A%20in%202008-2009%2C%202012%2C%202014%20and%20now%2C%20in%202023.%20No%20wonder%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2F13%2Fgazas-terrified-children-all-too-aware-israels-bombs-stole-their-joy%5C%22%3Eone%20of%20the%20channel%E2%80%99s%20reports%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20children%E2%80%99s%20ages%20are%20measured%20by%20how%20many%20Israeli%20assaults%20they%20have%20been%20through.%E2%80%9D%20Like%20a%20rite%20of%20passage%2C%20almost.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20trauma%20children%20in%20Gaza%20have%20suffered%20over%20the%20years%20has%20been%20documented%20in%20a%202022%20report%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fresourcecentre.savethechildren.net%2Fdocument%2Ftrapped-the-impact-of-15-years-of-blockade-on-the-mental-health-of-gazas-children%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETrapped%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20by%20Save%20the%20Children.%20The%20findings%20are%20not%20unexpected%3A%20%E2%80%9CFifteen%20years%20of%20life%20under%20blockade%20has%20left%20four%20out%20of%20five%20children%20in%20the%C2%A0Gaza%C2%A0Strip%C2%A0reporting%20that%20they%20live%20with%20depression%2C%20grief%20and%20fear.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%202022%20study%20found%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20mental%20wellbeing%20of%20children%2C%20young%20people%20and%20caregivers%20has%20dramatically%C2%A0deteriorated%20since%20a%20similar%20study%20in%202018%2C%20with%20the%20number%20of%20children%20reporting%20emotional%20distress%20increasing%20to%2080%25%20from%2055%25.%E2%80%9D%20More%20children%20said%20they%20were%20feeling%20%E2%80%9Cfearful%20(84%25%20compared%20to%2050%25%20in%202018)%2C%20sad%20or%20depressed%20(77%25%20compared%20to%2062%25)%20and%20grieving%20(78%25%20compared%20to%2055%25).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20telling%20finding%20was%20that%20more%20than%20half%20of%C2%A0Gaza%E2%80%99s%20children%20have%20contemplated%20suicide%C2%A0and%20three%20out%20of%20five%20are%20self-harming.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWars%20apart%2C%20for%20the%20last%2015%20years%2C%20the%20children%20of%20Gaza%20have%20been%20experiencing%20a%20land%2C%20air%20and%20sea%20blockade%20imposed%20by%20Israel.%20In%20fact%2C%20more%20than%20800%2C000%20children%20have%20never%20known%20a%20life%20without%20the%20blockade.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gaza%20War%20Marks%20the%20Complete%20Collapse%20of%20Policies%20Israel%20Has%20Pursued%20Over%20Several%20Decades%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fcomplete-collapse-policies-israel-hamas-war%5C%22%3EGaza%20War%20Marks%20the%20Complete%20Collapse%20of%20Policies%20Israel%20Has%20Pursued%20Over%20Several%20Decades%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20rampaging%20war%20on%20Gaza%20continues%2C%20backed%20by%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20hug%20and%20protestations%20of%20full%20support%20by%20European%20nations.%20Entire%20neighbourhoods%20flattened%2C%20bombed%20out%20of%20existence%3B%20the%20terrorising%20sound%20and%20shaking%20caused%20by%20missiles%20as%20they%20unerringly%20hit%20their%20targets%3B%20the%20constant%20news%20of%20the%20deaths%20of%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20their%20own%20bodies%20shattered%20by%20injuries%20%E2%80%93%20this%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98life%E2%80%99%20of%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20children%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20at%20work%2C%20reporting%20on%20the%20death%20and%20devastation%20being%20wrought%20by%20the%20Israeli%20assault%20on%20Gaza%2C%20and%20to%20find%20out%20that%20your%20son%2C%20daughter%20and%20grandchild%20have%20been%20killed%20by%20an%20Israeli%20airstrike%2C%20as%20happened%20with%20Wael%20Dahdouh%2C%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20chief%20correspondent%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%3B%20to%20be%20in%20the%20kitchen%20because%20your%20sweet%20boy%20with%20curly%20hair%20demanded%20dinner%2C%20and%20to%20never%20see%20him%20again%2C%20as%20happened%20with%20Yusuf%E2%80%99s%20mother%20Rawan%20%E2%80%93%20this%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98life%E2%80%99%20of%20parents%20in%20Gaza%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20families%20of%20Gaza%2C%20where%20children%20still%20have%20parents%20and%20parents%20still%20have%20children%2C%20fearful%20adults%20try%20to%20address%20the%20fears%20of%20their%20children%20as%20best%20as%20they%20can.%20An%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20mentions%20several%20instances.%20One%20parent%20consoles%20a%20child%20saying%20he%20has%20gone%20through%20similar%20circumstances%20and%20has%20come%20through%20the%20ordeal%3B%20another%20tells%20her%20children%20how%20to%20identify%20the%20light%20accompanying%20a%20missile%20so%20that%20they%20brace%20themselves%20for%20the%20sound%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20really%20b