2ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fharrdy-sandhu-once-got-rohit-sharma-ravindra-jadeja-out-video-goes-viral-4534372%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sophie%20spotted%20KISSING%20British%20millionaire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698826805000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104882448%2Cimgsize-42398.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fsophie-turner-spotted-kissing-british-millionaire-peregrine-pearson-in-paris-amidst-divorce-battle-with-joe-jonas%2Farticleshow%2F104881994.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104881994.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EGame%20of%20Thrones%20actress%20Sophie%20Turner%20was%20spotted%20kissing%20British%20aristocrat%20Peregrine%20Pearson%20in%20Paris%20amid%20her%20ongoing%20divorce%20battle%20with%20Joe%20Jonas.%20The%20alleged%20couple%20was%20seen%20passionately%20locking%20lips%20at%20the%20Gare%20du%20Nord%20railway%20station%20before%20reuniting%20at%20the%20city's%20stadium.%20Pearson%2C%20the%20heir%20to%20the%204th%20Viscount%20Cowdray%2C%20recently%20ended%20his%20relationship%20with%20Princess%20Maria-Olympia%20of%20Greece%20and%20Denmark.%20Turner%20and%20Jonas%20filed%20for%20divorce%20last%20month%20and%20have%20reached%20a%20temporary%20agreement%20regarding%20custody%20of%20their%20two%20daughters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fsophie-turner-spotted-kissing-british-millionaire-peregrine-pearson-in-paris-amidst-divorce-battle-with-joe-jonas%2Farticleshow%2F104881994.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI%20Education%20To%20Begin%20From%20Class%206%3A%20Here's%20All%20You%20Need%20To%20Know%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETo%20meet%20the%20rising%20demand%20for%20AI%20and%20data%20science%20knowledge%20in%20India%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20has%20introduced%20plans%20to%20incorporate%20AI%20courses%20into%20the%20country's%20educational%20curriculum.%20These%20courses%20will%20begin%20at%20the%20school%20level%2C%20starting%20from%20Class%206.%20A%20committee%20has%20developed%20a%20comprehensive%20curriculum%20for%20these%20courses%20under%20the%20'National%20Programme%20on%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(NPAI)%20Skilling%20Framework%2C'%20ensuring%20that%20students%20nationwide%20are%20adequately%20equipped%20for%20AI%20education.%20The%20estimated%20demand%20for%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2FData%20Science%20professionals%20in%20India%20is%20expected%20to%20exceed%201%20million%20by%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20committee's%20report%20in%20June%202023%20underscores%20the%20necessity%20of%20introducing%20AI%20education%20at%20various%20levels%20within%20the%20educational%20system.%20These%20courses%20will%20be%20aligned%20with%20both%20the%20National%20Higher%20Education%20Qualifications%20Framework%20and%20the%20National%20Credit%20Framework%2C%20ensuring%20a%20consistent%20approach%20to%20AI%20education%20across%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20ethical%20considerations%20within%20AI%20education%2C%20recommending%20that%20at%20least%2010%20percent%20of%20the%20course%20duration%20be%20dedicated%20to%20ethical%20aspects.%20This%20approach%20aims%20to%20promote%20responsible%20development%20and%20deployment%20of%20AI%20systems%2C%20with%20an%20emphasis%20on%20transparency%2C%20fairness%2C%20and%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ugc.gov.in%2Fpdfnews%2F5732498_Report-on-NPAI-Skilling-Framework.pdf%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20to%20access%20the%20report%20on%20National%20Programme%20on%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(NPAI)%20Skilling%20Framework%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20keep%20pace%20with%20the%20rapidly%20evolving%20field%20of%20AI%2C%20the%20report%20highlights%20the%20importance%20of%20flexible%20course%20development.%20It%20suggests%20creating%20smaller%20modules%2C%20such%20as%20micro-credentials%2C%20to%20adapt%20to%20technological%20advancements.%20Regulatory%20bodies%2C%20including%20the%20National%20Council%20for%20Vocational%20Education%20and%20Training%2C%20the%20All%20India%20Council%20for%20Technical%20Education%2C%20and%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%2C%20have%20been%20tasked%20with%20establishing%20guidelines%20and%20standards%20for%20AI%20education.%20You%20can%20access%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ugc.gov.in%2Fpdfnews%2F5732498_Report-on-NPAI-Skilling-Framework.pdf%5C%22%3Ereports%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission's%20website%20at%20www.ugc.gov.in.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20NASSCOM%20report%20identified%20a%2051%20per%20cent%20shortfall%20in%20the%20demand%20and%20supply%20of%20AI%20and%20disruptive%20technology%20capabilities%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20introduction%20of%20AI%20courses%20in%20schools%20and%20undergraduate%20programs.%20The%20carefully%20crafted%2C%20age-appropriate%20school%20curriculum%20covers%20essential%20AI%20principles%2C%20machine%20learning%2C%20data%20management%2C%20programming%2C%20and%20ethical%20considerations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20report%20proposes%20faculty%20development%20programs%20to%20enhance%20educators'%20understanding%20of%20AI%20concepts%20and%20teaching%20methodologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECurrent%20status%3A%20AI%20skilling%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVarious%20AI%20skill%20courses%20are%20currently%20available%2C%20with%20additional%20courses%20continually%20being%20developed.%20Within%20the%20government's%20skill%20development%20network%2C%20courses%20are%20offered%20by%20entities%20such%20as%20Future%20Skills%20Prime%20(overseen%20by%20the%20NASSCOM%20Sector%20Skill%20Council)%2C%20NPTEL%2C%20Centre%20of%20Advanced%20Studies%20(CDAC)%2C%20and%20NIELIT.%20These%20courses%20cater%20to%20students%20at%20the%20school%20level%2C%20and%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20courses%20are%20also%20accessible%20through%20AICTE%20accredited%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETraining%20of%20assessors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20assessments%20will%20be%20categorised%20into%20four%20groups%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKnowledge-based%20assessments%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20These%20evaluations%20are%20expected%20to%20consist%20of%20multiple-choice%20questions%20or%20interactive%20environments%20that%20can%20be%20automatically%20graded.%20Subject%20matter%20experts%20(SMEs)%20will%20design%20these%20assessments%2C%20adhering%20to%20robust%20assessment%20design%20principles.%20To%20facilitate%20these%20assessments%2C%20proctors%20will%20need%20training%20for%20administration.%20These%20assessments%20can%20be%20conducted%20in%20both%20formative%20and%20summative%20formats%20based%20on%20specific%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EApplication-based%20assessments%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20These%20assessments%20will%20be%20conducted%20by%20college%20or%20undergraduate%20students%20and%20will%20be%20evaluated%20by%20college%20faculty%20members%20in%20collaboration%20with%20industry%20partners%20who%20will%20establish%20standardized%20norms%20and%20criteria%20for%20assessment.%20The%20assessors%20themselves%20will%20receive%20training%20from%20the%20industry%20or%20in%20accordance%20with%20institutional%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndustry%20certifications%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20These%20assessments%20will%20follow%20the%20standards%20set%20by%20the%20industry%20or%20original%20equipment%20manufacturers%20(OEMs).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProjects%2C%20hackathons%2C%20and%20internships%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20These%20eva