icalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khans-jawan-to-stream-on-ott-from-this-date%2Farticleshow%2F104882064.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BLACKPINK's%20Lisa%E2%80%99s%20Weibo%20account%20terminated%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698824508000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104881987%2Cimgsize-28058.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fblackpinks-lisas-weibo-account-terminated-report%2Farticleshow%2F104881871.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104881871.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBLACKPINK%20member%20Lisa's%20personal%20Weibo%20account%20has%20mysteriously%20disappeared%2C%20leaving%20fans%20in%20shock.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20account%20was%20terminated%20due%20to%20alleged%20violations%20of%20Weibo's%20rules%2C%20following%20backlash%20from%20her%20recent%20performance%20at%20a%20club.%20Neither%20Lisa%20nor%20Weibo%20has%20made%20official%20statements%20regarding%20the%20account's%20termination%2C%20leaving%20fans%20in%20suspense.%20Lisa's%20participation%20in%20the%20Crazy%20Horse%20shows%20had%20generated%20significant%20anticipation%20and%20support%20from%20fans%20and%20celebrities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fblackpinks-lisas-weibo-account-terminated-report%2Farticleshow%2F104881871.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Green%20Hydrogen%20Initiatives%20Risk%20Increased%20Pollution%20Without%20Strict%20Carbon%20Accounting%20Rules%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F31135906%2F15010336808_383bd10b55_b.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%20is%20investing%20heavily%20in%20green%20hydrogen%20initiatives.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20government%20has%20earmarked%20over%20Rs%2019%2C000%20crores%20to%20make%20India%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmnre.gov.in%2Fnational-green-hydrogen-mission%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cthe%20global%20hub%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20green%20hydrogen%20energy%20production%2C%20use%20and%20export.%20But%20if%20strict%20rules%20are%20not%20put%20in%20place%2C%20our%20green%20hydrogen%20initiatives%20could%20end%20up%20adding%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20carbon%20emissions%20and%20polluting%20the%20environment%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fclimateriskhorizons.com%2Fresearch%2FGreen-Hydrogen.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epublished%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20Bengaluru-based%20think-tank%20Climate%20Risk%20Horizons%20on%20October%2026.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20green%20hydrogen%20push%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAround%2070%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20power%20needs%20currently%20are%20derived%20from%20coal%2C%20a%20polluting%20fossil%20fuel.%20India%2C%20like%20most%20of%20the%20world%2C%20is%20looking%20to%20increase%20its%20sources%20of%20renewable%20energy.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20green%20hydrogen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGreen%20hydrogen%20is%20hydrogen%20produced%20by%20splitting%20water%20into%20hydrogen%20and%20oxygen%20using%20renewable%20electricity%20(as%20opposed%20to%20grey%20hydrogen%2C%20which%20is%20generated%20using%20natural%20gas%20or%20coal%20or%20other%20polluting%20fossil%20fuels).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmnre.gov.in%2Fnational-green-hydrogen-mission%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaim%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20National%20Green%20Hydrogen%20Mission%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20New%20and%20Renewable%20Energy%20(MNRE)%20is%20to%20make%20India%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20global%20hub%E2%80%9D%20of%20production%2C%20use%20and%20export%20of%20green%20hydrogen%20and%20its%20derivatives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%207%2C%20the%20MNRE%20released%20a%20research%20and%20development%20%E2%80%9Croadmap%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20Green%20Hydrogen%20Mission%2C%20budgeted%20at%20Rs%20400%20crore%20for%202-3%20years%20alone.%20As%20per%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmnre.gov.in%2Fnational-green-hydrogen-mission%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMNRE%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20initial%20outlay%20for%20the%20mission%20will%20be%20Rs%2019%2C744%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20includes%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2017%2C490%20crore%20for%20the%20Strategic%20Interventions%20for%20Green%20Hydrogen%20Transition%20(SIGHT)%20programme%20which%20aims%20to%20incentivise%20green%20hydrogen%20production%20and%20electrolyser%20manufacturing%20(electrolysers%20are%20a%20critical%20part%20of%20producing%20hydrogen%3B%20the%20device%20helps%20split%20water%20into%20its%20hydrogen%20and%20oxygen%20components%20using%20a%20chemical%20process).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20amount%20of%20Rs%201%2C466%20crore%20is%20earmarked%20for%20pilot%20projects%2C%20Rs%20400%20crore%20for%20research%20and%20development%2C%20and%20Rs%20388%20crore%20%E2%80%9Ctowards%20other%20Mission%20components%E2%80%9D%2C%20per%20the%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20website.%20The%20Ministry%20also%20launched%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nsws.gov.in%2Fportal%2Fscheme%2Fgreenhydrogenpolicy%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enational%20single%20window%20system%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20approvals%20under%20the%20mission.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWord%20of%20caution%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20green%20hydrogen%20push%20could%20end%20up%20increasing%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20carbon%20emissions%20unless%20the%20right%20safeguards%20and%20proper%20carbon%20accounting%20systems%20are%20put%20in%20place%2C%20cautioned%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fclimateriskhorizons.com%2Fresearch%2FGreen-Hydrogen.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20published%20by%20Bengaluru-based%20energy%20think-tank%20Climate%20Risk%20Horizons.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20electrolysers%20are%20run%20day%20and%20night%20(as%20there%20will%20be%20pressure%20to)%2C%20they%20will%20operate%20even%20during%20times%20when%20no%20renewable%20energy%20is%20being%20generated.%20For%20instance%2C%20they%20will%20also%20run%20at%20night%C2%A0%20when%20there%20is%20no%20solar%20power%20generation.%20If%20this%20electricity%20comes%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20coal-powered%20grid%20then%2C%20it%20will%20only%20add%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20carbon%20emissions%20rather%20than%20decrease%20them%2C%20the%20report%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGreen%20hydrogen%20produced%20this%20way%2C%20the%20report%20noted%2C%20would%20make%20it%20even%20more%20polluting%20than%20conventional%20grey%20hydrogen%20due%20to%20its%20embodied%20emissions%20(greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%20released%20during%20the%20production%20of%20a%20good).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20because%20India%20is%20currently%20dependent%20on%20coal-generated%20power.%20and%20it%20is%20this%20that%20India%20and%20the%20world%20are%20trying%20to%20phase%20down%20to%20decrease%20emissions%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%2C%20a%20polluting%20greenhouse%20gas%20that%20contributes%20to%20global%20warming%20which%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20causes%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20also%20problems%20with%20MNRE%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1950421%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAfter%2520discussions%2520with%2520multiple%2520stakeholders%2C2%2520equivalent%2520%252F%2520kg%2520H2.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edefinition%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20per%20the%20report.%20The%20current%20definition%20%E2%80%9Cleaves%20a%20lot%20to%20interpretation%E2%80%9D%2C%20such%20as%20raising%20questions%20whether%20it%20includes%20embodied%20emissions%20of%20the%20type%20of%20electricity%20being%20used%20to%20generate%20the%20green%20hydrogen.%20Per%20the%20report%2C%20the%20MNRE%20definition%20also%20includes%20the%20use%20of%20biomass%2C%20or%20organic%20matter%20from%20plants%20and%20waste%2C%20in%20producing%20green%20hydrogen.%20This%2C%20the%20report%20says%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9Cproblematic%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20carbon%20emissions%20from%20the%20gasification%20process%2C%20and%20the%20source%20of%20the%20biomass%20itself%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENeed%20for%20a%20proper%20carbon%20accounting%20system%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20MNRE%20is%20yet%20to%20finalise%20the%20accounting%20or%20certification%20methods%20for%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20per%20the%20report.%20Everything%20now%20rests%20on%20a%20proper%20accounting%20system%20%E2%80%93%20a%20poor%20system%20would%20subsidise%20the%20production%20of%20green%20hydrogen%20that%20is%20more%20carbon%20intensive%20than%20even%20conventional%20grey%20hydrogen%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWeak%20guidelines%20for%20green%20hydrogen%20will%20squander%20the%20promise%20and%20effectiveness%20of%20truly%20green%20hydrogen%20as%20a%20decarbonisation%20tool%20and%20will%20probably%20increase%20emissions%2C%20which%20is%20in%20direct%20conflict%20with%20the%20aims%20of%20the%20green%20hydrogen%20mission%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20noted.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20could%20also%20jeopardise%20India%E2%80%99s%20clean%20hydrogen%20industry%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20as%20a%20polluting%20and%20contentious%20start%20to%20the%20sector%20would%20damage%20international%20credibility%2C%20reduce%20access%20to%20export%20markets%20and%20undermine%20public%20trust.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20essential%20that%20the%20MNRE%20gets%20this%20%5Baccounting%20system%2F%20methodology%5D%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ashish%20Fernandes%2C%20CEO%20of%20Climate%20Risk%20Horizons%2C%20in%20a%20press%20release.%20%E2%80%9CGreen%20Hydrogen%20has%20massive%20potential%20to%20reduce%20carbon%20emissions%20from%20industrial%20sectors%2C%20but%20only%20if%20the%20accounting%20methods%20and%20safeguards%20are%20rigorous.%20This%20means%20it%20has%20to%20be%20powered%20100%25%20by%20new%2C%20additional%20renewable%20energy%20that%20is%20matched%20to%20consumption%20on%20an%20hourly%20basis.%20If%20the%20rules%20have%20loopholes%2C%20either%20by%20allowing%20RE%20%5BRenewable%20Energy%5D%20credits%20or%20matching%20consumption%20with%20RE%20generation%20on%20a%20monthly%20or%20annual%20basis%2C%20it%20will%20not%20deliver%20actual%20carbon%20reductions.%20This%20will%20undermine%20the%20green%20hydrogen%20market%20before%20it%20can%20even%20get%20started.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20risk%20that%20RE%20for%20green%20hydrogen%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20crowd%20out%20needed%20investment%20in%20grid%20RE%2C%20with%20negative%20consequences%20in%20terms%20of%20meeting%20India%E2%80%99s%20climate%20commitments%E2%80%9D%2C%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cconstrained%20environment%20with%20high%20cost%20of%20capital%E2%80%9D%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%20renewable%20energy%20target%20of%20450%20GW%20by%202030%20already%20requires%20huge%20investment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Fernandes%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20green%20hydrogen%20mission%20will%20require%20an%20additional%20125%20GW%20of%20RE.%20The%20MNRE%20needs%20to%20guard%20against%20the%20risk%20that%20finance%20for%20RE%20projects%20that%20would%20otherwise%20decarbonise%20the%20electricity%20grid%20will%20instead%20be%20diverted%20to%20produce%20green%20hydrogen.%20This%20would%20delay%20India%E2%80%99s%20journey%20to%20net%20zero%2C%20undermine%20a%20nascent%20industry%20and%20deny%20states%20and%20electricity%20consumers%20the%20cost%20benefits%20that%20cheap%20renewable%20energy%20has%20to%20offer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBig%20corporations%20including%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20TATA%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%2C%20etc%20have%20unveiled%20plans%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20green%20hydrogen%20industry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698824368000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F31135906%2F15010336808_383bd10b55_b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenergy%2Findias-green-hydrogen-initiatives-risk-increased-pollution-without-strict-carbon-accounting-rules%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Everything%20now%20rests%20on%20the%20MNRE%20getting%20its%20carbon%20accounting%20system%20right%20so%20that%20green%20hydrogen%20produced%20in%20India%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20end%20up%20being%20a%20worse%20polluter%20than%20coal-generated%20hydrogen%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenergy%2Findias-green-hydrogen-initiatives-risk-increased-pollution-without-strict-carbon-accounting-rules%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20How%20New%20India-Bangladesh%20Rail%20Link%20Will%20Bring%20Northeast%20Closer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3ECurrently%2C%20travelling%20from%20Kolkata%20to%20Tripura's%20capital%20Agartala%20by%20train%20takes%20passengers%20on%20a%20long%2C%20circuitous%20route%20via%20northern%20West%20Bengal%20to%20Guwahati%20in%20Assam.%20The%20route%20then%20turns%20so