nning%20run%20of%20six%20matches.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Babar%20Azam%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59905-mohammad-babar-azam-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBabar%20Azam%3C%2Fa%3E-led%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20are%20in%20tricky%20spot%20with%20only%20three%20wins%20in%20seven%20matches.%20Their%20chances%20of%20entering%20the%20semi-final%20are%20slim.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20midst%20of%20this%2C%20former%20Pakistan%20allrounder%C2%A0%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Abdul%20Razzaq%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F95-abdul-razzaq-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAbdul%20Razzaq%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20asked%20a%20question%20on%20an%20Youtube%C2%A0channel%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dlu3sKQ0dQeQ%26t%3D467s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E'Hasna%20Mana%20Hai'%3C%2Fa%3E%20regarding%20an%20old%20comment%20of%20his%2C%20where%20he%20called%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20'baby%20bowler'.%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20has%20been%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20Indian%20bowling%20attack%20at%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%2C%20with%20his%20latest%20fine%20show%20coming%20against%20England.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcricketpakistan.com.pk%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2Fi-would-have-easily-dominated-bumrah-razzaq%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECricket%20Pakistan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Abdul%20Razzaq%20had%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20played%20against%20great%20bowlers%20like%20Glenn%20Mcgrath%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Wasim%20Akram%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F438-wasim-akram-playerprofile%5C%22%3EWasim%20Akram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20Bumrah%20is%20a%20baby%20bowler%20in%20front%20of%20me%20and%20I%20could%20have%20easily%20dominated%20and%20attacked%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20TV%20show%2C%20Abdul%20Razzaq%20was%20asked%20about%20his%20comments%20considering%20his%20performance%20in%20the%20World%20Cup.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhatever%20I%20said%2C%20it%20was%20interpreted%20in%20the%20wrong%20way.%20The%20question%20was%20how%20do%20you%20see%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Glenn%20McGrath%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F292-glenn-mcgrath-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGlenn%20McGrath%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Wasim%20Akram%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20Shoaib%20Akhtar.%20%3Cem%3EUnke%20samne%2C%20woh%20baby%20bowler%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(He%20is%20a%20baby%20bowler%20%C2%A0in%20front%20of%20them)%20%3Cem%3EMaine%20ye%20kabhi%20nhi%20kaha%20ki%20Bumrah%20acha%20bowler%20nhi%20hai.%20Par%20jab%20aap%20unhe%3C%2Fem%3E%20Wasim%20Akram%2C%20Glenn%20McGrath%20%3Cem%3Ese%20compare%20karenge%20to%20unhe%20baby%20bowler%20na%20kahu%20to%20aur%20kya%20kahu%3C%2Fem%3E.%20(I%20have%20never%20said%20that%20he%20is%20not%20a%20good%20bowler.%20But%20if%20you%20compare%20him%20with%20Wasim%20Akram%2C%20Glenn%20McGrath%2C%20you%20tell%20me%20if%20I%20am%20wrong%20in%20calling%20him%20baby%20bowler).%20%3Cem%3EJab%20main%20team%20main%20aaya%20tha%2C%20main%20bhi%20bachcha%20tha%20Wasim%20Akram%20ke%20samne%3C%2Fem%3E%20(When%20I%20came%20into%20the%20Pakistan%20team%2C%20I%20was%20also%20a%20baby%20in%20front%20of%20Wasim%20Akram)%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Razzaq.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Bumrah%20has%20often%20been%20compared%20with%20Pakistan's%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shaheen%20Afridi%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108785-shaheen-afridi-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShaheen%20Afridi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20former%20Pakistan%20pace%20great%20Wasim%20Akram%20seems%20to%20have%20completely%20ended%20that%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20the%20best%20in%20the