hone-hacking-message-cert-multiple-vulnerabilities-warning-days-before-apples-threat-message-4534016%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Experts%20Urge%20Union%20Govt%20to%20Be%20Transparent%20About%20ICMR%20Data%20Breach%20Probe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F16160905%2Fdata_breach.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EOpposition%20leaders%20and%20cybersecurity%20experts%20have%20urged%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20act%20swiftly%20and%20transparently%20in%20its%20probe%20into%20the%20breach%20of%20personal%20data%20pertaining%20to%2081.5%20crore%20Indians%20from%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20servers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Findians-personal-data-breached-yet-again-but-no-sign-that-gaps-will-be-plugged%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20breach%20came%20to%20light%20after%20a%20US%20cybersecurity%20firm%20brought%20the%20following%20details%20to%20light%3A%20A%20threat%20actor%20with%20the%20alias%20%E2%80%98pwn0001%E2%80%99%20claimed%20that%20they%20could%20sell%20records%20of%20815%20million%20Indians%2C%20including%20names%2C%20ages%2C%20phone%20numbers%2C%20Aadhaar%20numbers%20and%20addresses.%20pwn0001%20shared%20a%20sample%2C%20which%20had%201%20lakh%20phone%20numbers%20and%20Aadhaar%20numbers.%20The%20sample%20dataset%20includes%20personal%20information%20of%20children%20as%20young%20as%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMishi%20Choudhary%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20Software%20Freedom%20Law%20Centre%20(SFLC)%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20more%20government%20agencies%20and%20companies%20hoovering%20up%20greater%20volumes%20of%20data%20now%20than%20ever%2C%20data%20leaks%20are%20almost%20inevitable.%20Any%20entity%20collecting%20such%20data%20should%20use%20data-centric%20security%20and%20deploy%20zero-trust%20protocols.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWithout%20a%20data%20security%20plan%2C%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20see%20sensitive%20personal%20information%20like%20health%20and%20financial%20data%20being%20breached.%20This%20will%20lead%20to%20identity%20theft%20and%20other%20costs%20amounting%20to%20billions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20opposition%20parties%20and%20experts%20pointed%20out%20that%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20an%20Indian%20government%20server%20has%20been%20breached%20and%20citizens%E2%80%99%20personal%20data%20compromised.%20%E2%80%9CAadhaar-based%20frauds%20have%20become%20quite%20common%20in%20India%20and%20yet%2C%20the%20regulator%20won%E2%80%99t%20address%20the%20problem%20at%20hand.%20UIDAI%20has%20virtually%20ignored%20the%20Aadhaar%20data%20leaks%2C%20while%20promising%20us%20a%20virtual%20ID%20solution%20that%20disappeared%20after%20the%20litigation%20around%20Aadhaar%20concluded%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srinivas%20Kodali%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Findians-personal-data-breached-yet-again-but-no-sign-that-gaps-will-be-plugged%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20asked%20on%20X%20why%20%E2%80%9Ccitizens%20%5Bare%5D%20left%20exposed%20and%20vulnerable%20to%20such%20data%20breaches%20when%20your%20%5BNarendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%5D%20government%20touts%20its%20commitment%20to%20ironclad%20data%20security%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20named%20individual%20ministers%20responsible%20for%20citizens%E2%80%99%20security%2C%20and%20also%20asked%20how%20the%20home%20ministry%20was%20%E2%80%9Cblissfully%20unaware%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20breach.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20massive%20Aadhaar%20data%20breach%2C%20personal%20identifiable%20information%20of%2081.5%20crore%20Indians%20has%20been%20leaked%20on%20the%20dark%20web.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20data%20breach.%20In%20June%2C%20personal%20details%20of%20ALL%20vaccinated%20Indians%20had%20been%20leaked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhy%2C%20PM%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narendramodi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20citizens%20left%20exposed%20and%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20All%20India%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(%40AITCofficial)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAITCofficial%2Fstatus%2F1719241507440570693%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2031%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698821228000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F16160905%2Fdata_breach.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fexperts-urge-union-govt-to-be-transparent-about-icmr-data-breach-probe%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mishi%20Choudhary%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20Software%20Freedom%20Law%20Centre%20(SFLC)%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20more%20government%20agencies%20and%20companies%20hoovering%20up%20greater%20volumes%20of%20data%20now%20than%20ever%2C%20data%20leaks%20are%20almost%20inevitable.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fexperts-urge-union-govt-to-be-transparent-about-icmr-data-breach-probe%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Charged%20With%20Manslaughter%20For%20Hate%20Crime%20In%20Fatal%20Attack%20On%20Sikh%20In%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man%20who%20attacked%20an%20elderly%20Sikh%20person%20during%20a%20car%20accident%20in%20New%20York%2C%20repeatedly%20calling%20him%20%26quot%3Bturban%20man%26quot%3B%20and%20fatally%20beating%20him%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20manslaughter%20and%20assault%20as%20hate%20crimes%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGilbert%20Augustin%20was%20arraigned%20on%20Tuesday%20on%20an%20indictment%20charging%20him%20with%20manslaughter%20and%20assault%20as%20hate%20crimes%20in%20the%20death%20of%2066-year-old%20Jasmer%20Singh%2C%20whom%20he%20attacked%20after%20a%20fender%20bender%20in%20Kew%20Gardens%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20of%20Queens%2C%20District%20Attorney%20Melinda%20Katz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20dispute%20that%20preceded%20the%20fatal%20beating%2C%20Augustin%20is%20accused%20of%20repeatedly%20referring%20to%20Jasmer%20Singh%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bturban%20man%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20case%20of%20a%20fender%20bender%20immediately%20escalating%20to%20hateful%20language%20and%20then%20brutal%2C%20deadly%20violence.%20We%20will%20show%20in%20court%20that%20it%20was%20a%20rage%20inflamed%20by%20hate%20that%20led%20to%20this%20senseless%20tragedy.%20The%20defendant%20will%20have%20to%20answer%20to%20some%20very%20serious%20charges%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Katz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAugustin%20faces%20up%20to%2025%20years%20in%20prison%20if%20convicted.%20Queens%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Kenneth%20Holder%20ordered%20him%20to%20return%20to%20court%20on%20December%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20October%2019%20attack%20on%20Singh%2C%20which%20led%20to%20his%20death%2C%20came%20just%20days%20after%20a%2019-year-old%20Sikh%20boy%20was%20attacked%20by%20Christopher%20Philippeaux%2C%2026%2C%20while%20he%20was%20riding%20the%20bus%20in%20Richmond%20Hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPhilippeaux%20punched%20the%20Sikh%20teenager%20in%20the%20back%20of%20the%20head%2C%20tried%20to%20knock%20off%20his%20turban%20and%20told%20him%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20wear%20that%20in%20this%20country.%26quot%3B%20Philippeaux%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20assault%20as%20a%20hate%20crime%20and%20aggravated%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Sikh%20community%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20recent%20incidents%20of%20hate%20crime%20and%20assault%2C%20New%20York%20City%20Mayor%20Eric%20Adams%20vowed%20to%20protect%20members%20of%20the%20community%20and%20gave%20a%20clarion%20call%20for%20educating%20people%20about%20Sikhism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Adams%20and%20New%20York%20State%20Assemblywoman%20Jenifer%20Rajkumar%20met%20and%20addressed%20members%20of%20the%20Sikh%20community%20at%20the%20Baba%20Makhan%20Shah%20Lubana%20Sikh%20Centre%20in%20the%20Queens%20neighbourhood%20of%20South%20Richmond%20Hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20not%20about%20terror%2C%20you%20are%20about%20protector.%20That%20is%20what%20needs%20to%20be%20taught%20throughout%20this%20entire%20city.%20Our%20young%20people%20need%20to%20know%20that%2C%20our%20adults%20need%20to%20know%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Adams%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribing%20Sikhs%20as%20%26quot%3Bprotectors%26quot%3B%20of%20society%2C%20Rajkumar%20asserted%20that%20the%20hateful%20targeting%20of%20Sikhs%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20acceptable%26quot%3B%20and%20perpetrators%20of%20such%20violence%20will%20be%20prosecuted%20to%20the%20fullest%20extent%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20use%20the%20levers%20of%20government%20to%20end%20hate%20crimes%20against%20Sikh%20Americans.%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20come%20together%20and%E2%80%A6educate%E2%80%A6%20New%20York%20State%2C%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20entire%20world%20about%20who%20the%20Sikh%20people%20truly%20are%20so%20we%20are%20not%20attacked%20and%20misunderstood%2C%26quot%3B%20Rajkumar%2C%20the%20first%20Indian-American%20woman%20elected%20to%20New%20York%20State%20Office%20and%20who%20described%20herself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bdaughter%20of%20Punjab%26quot%3B%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajkumar%20had%20said%20this%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20she%20had%20visited%20the%20Gurudwara%20and%20had%20spoken%20out%20against%20hate%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20it%20is%20the%20last%20time%20I%20want%20to%20be%20standing%20here%20speaking%20out%20against%20hate%20crimes.%20Starting%20now%20we%20are%20going%20to%20end%20the%20hateful%20targeting%20of%20Sikhs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESingh's%20son%20Subeg%20Singh%20Multani%2C%20an%20immigration%20attorney%2C%20who%20was%20also%20present%20at%20the%20event%20on%20Sunday%2C%20had%20said%20that%20the%20attack%20on%20his%20father%20should%20be%20pursued%20as%20a%20hate%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMultani%2C%20who%20became%20emotional%20and%20choked%20up%20as%20he%20addressed%20the%20gathering%2C%20said%20his%20father%20came%20from%20India%20to%20the%20US%20in%20the%20early%201990s%20with%20the%20American%20dream%20in%20his%20eyes.%20%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20know%20that%20the%20dream%20would%20be%20shattered%20the%20way%20it%20has%20shattered%26quot%3B%20on%20October%2019%20in%20this%20%26quot%3Bgreat%26quot%3B%20and%20diverse%20city%20of%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMultani%20had%20called%20on%20members%20of%20the%20community%20to%20join%20him%20in%20court%20for%20Augustin's%20arraignment.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20show%20the%20solidarity%20and%20unity%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20judge.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20show%20them%20this%20is%20a%20hate%20crime.%20This%20case%20must%20be%20pursued%20as%20a%20hate%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20charges%20in%20the%20case%2C%20late%20morning%20on%20October%2019%2C%20Singh%20was%20driving%20a%20vehicle%20that%20collided%20with%20Augustin's%20car.%20Immediately%20following%20the%20collision%2C%20Singh%20and%20Augustin%20pulled%20over%20to%20assess%20the%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20witness%20observed%20Augustin%20get%20out%20of%20his%20car%20and%20approach%20Singh%2C%20who%20remained%20seated%20in%20his%20vehicle%20and%20engaged%20in%20a%20verbal%20dispute%20with%20the%20victim.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20dispute%2C%20the%20witness%20heard%20Augustin%20say%20to%20Singh%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%20police%2C%20no%20police.%26quot%3B%20The%20witness%20also%20heard%20Augustin%20repeatedly%20refer%20to%20Singh%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BTurban%20man.%26quot%3B%20While%20arguing%20angrily%20with%20Singh%2C%20Augustin%20told%20the%20victim%20that%20he%20was%20not%20going%20to%20allow%20him%20to%20go%20home%20and%20did%20not%20want%20him%20to%20call%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20witness%20testimony%20and%20video%20surveillance%2C%20Augustin%20reached%20into%20Singh's%20car%20and%20grabbed%20Singh's%20cell%20phone.%20Singh%20got%20out%20of%20his%20car%20and%20followed%20Augustin%2C%20who%20appeared%20to%20be%20holding%20two%20phones.%20The%20pair%20appeared%20to%20argue.%20Singh%20eventually%20recovered%20his%20phone%2C%20prosecutors%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Singh%20was%20walking%20back%20to%20his%20car%2C%20Augustin%20punched%20him%20three%20times%20in%20the%20head%20and%20face.%20One%20of%20the%20punches%20caused%20Singh's%20turban%20to%20come%20flying%20off%20his%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20the%20blows%2C%20Singh%20fell%20backwards%20to%20the%20ground%2C%20the%20back%20of%20his%20head%20hitting%20the%20pavement.%20Singh%20suffered%20a%20brain%20injury%20and%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20hospital.%20He%20died%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20said%20that%20after%20striking%20Singh%2C%20Augustin%20got%20into%20his%20car%20and%20drove%20away.%20The%20day%20after%20the%20assault%2C%20a%20New%20York%20Police%20Department%20officer%20saw%20Augustin%20sitting%20in%20his%20car%20in%20Jamaica.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAugustin%20was%20unable%20to%20produce%20a%20valid%20driver's%20license%20or%20insurance.%20A%20review%20of%20motor%20vehicle%20records%20showed%20his%20driver's%20license%20was%20suspended.%20He%20was%20taken%20into%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAugustin%2C%2030%2C%20of%20111th%20Avenue%20in%20Jamaica%2C%20was%20charged%20in%20a%2020-count%20indictment.%20The%20charges%20include%20manslaughter%20in%20the%20first%20degree%20as%20a%20hate%20crime%3B%20assault%20in%20the%20second%20degree%20as%20a%20hate%20crime%3B%20two%20counts%20of%20operating%20or%20driving%20a%20motor%20vehicle%20without%20a%20license%3B%20leaving%20the%20scene%20of%20an%20incident%20without%20reporting%20and%20reckless%20driving.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698821040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fvls8dias_sikh-man-jasmer-singh-beaten-to-death-in-new-york_625x300_01_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-charged-with-manslaughter-for-hate-crime-in-fatal-attack-on-sikh-in-new-york-4533868%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20man%20who%20attacked%20an%20elderly%20Sikh%20person%20during%20a%20car%20accident%20in%20New%20York%2C%20repeatedly%20calling%20him%20%26quot%3Bturban%20man%26quot%3B%20and%20fatally%20beating%20him%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20manslaughter%20and%20assault%20as%20hate%20crimes%2C%20prosecutors%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-charged-with-manslaughter-for-hate-crime-in-fatal-attack-on-sikh-in-new-york-4533868%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-charged-with-manslaughter-for-hate-crime-in-fatal-attack-on-sikh-in-new-york-4533868%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-charged-with-manslaughter-for-hate-crime-in-fatal-attack-on-sikh-in-new-york-4533868%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Joram%20to%20CLASH%20with%20Animal%2C%20Sam%20Bahadur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698821015000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104880128%2Cimgsize-48128.cm