20including%20phones%2C%20hard%20disks%2C%20laptops%20and%20even%20passports%2C%20of%20over%2090%20journalists%20who%20were%20interrogated%20and%20whose%20homes%20were%20searched%20on%20October%203%2C%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20majority%20of%20them%20were%20either%20freelancers%20who%20were%20or%20had%20occasionally%20been%20contributing%20writers%20or%20did%20video%20shows%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20of%20them%20were%20former%20employees%20who%20are%20currently%20employed%20in%20different%20organisations.%20Only%20a%20small%20number%20are%20still%20on%20the%20direct%20payroll%20of%20the%20website.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20senior%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20staffer%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%2090%20people%20whose%20devices%20are%20taken%20away%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20case.%20A%20storage%20device%20with%20all%20the%20archival%20footage%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20also%20gone.%20Overall%2C%20about%20250%20devices%20belonging%20to%2090%20people%20are%20with%20the%20police.%20Many%20individuals%20have%20had%20up%20to%20three%20devices%20taken%20away.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20number%20of%20devices%20is%20so%20large.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20staffer%20also%20said%20that%20none%20of%20the%20people%20whose%20devices%20were%20seized%20by%20the%20police%20were%20given%20the%20mandatory%20hash%20values%20of%20their%20electronic%20items%2C%20as%20prescribed%20by%20the%20courts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20added%20that%20while%20some%20of%20them%20were%20given%20seizure%20memos%2C%20most%20of%20them%20were%20denied%20even%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FJoGxsZrhAGY%3Fsi%3Dar2uiOF7O-dqZSg1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20absence%20of%20these%20original%20devices%2C%20which%20are%20a%20storehouse%20of%20phone%20numbers%20and%20contact%20details%20for%20any%20working%20journalist%2C%20the%20journalists%20have%20been%20facing%20acute%20problems%20in%20continuing%20with%20their%20work%20according%20to%20their%20usual%20routines.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20are%20using%20second-hand%20laptops%20or%20phones%2C%20while%20some%20have%20borrowed%20working%20devices%20from%20their%20friends%20to%20carry%20on%20their%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20another%20senior%20staffer%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJournalists%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20described%20their%20current%20ordeal%20as%20a%20blow%20to%20essential%20work%20for%20a%20digital%20journalism%20platform%20like%20theirs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20field%20notes%20have%20gone%20with%20the%20devices.%20It%20is%20an%20arduous%20task%20to%20compile%20information%20from%20years%20of%20fieldwork.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20expect%20the%20police%20to%20understand%2C%20but%20at%20least%20the%20courts%20should%20understand%20the%20significance%20of%20such%20field%20notes%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20journalists%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20one%20such%20freelancer%20who%20was%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20the%20Delhi%20police%E2%80%99s%20raids%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20of%20them%20were%20told%20by%20the%20police%20that%20their%20devices%20will%20be%20returned%20anywhere%20between%20two%20days%20to%20a%20month%20after%20due%20examination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20specific%20pattern%20followed%20by%20the%20police%20regarding%20the%20assurance%20that%20they%20gave%20to%20journalists%20before%20taking%20their%20devices%20away.%20However%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20communication%20from%20the%20police%20about%20the%20possible%20date%20of%20return%20of%20the%20devices%20since%20October%203.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20have%20moved%20the%20court%20to%20secure%20our%20devices%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20senior%20staffer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnewsclick-case-if-modi-government-is-really-serious-about-terror-financing-why-havent-they-rung-the-us-china-and-fatf%5C%22%3ENewsClick%20Case%3A%20If%20Modi%20Govt%20is%20Really%20Serious%20About%20%E2%80%98Terror%20Financing%E2%80%99%2C%20Why%20Hasn%E2%80%99t%20It%20Rung%20the%20US%2C%20China%20and%20FATF%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecent%20experiences%20indicate%20that%20despite%20such%20immediate%20assurances%2C%20the%20police%20has%20been%20reluctant%20in%20returning%20the%20seized%20electronic%20devices.%20Recently%2C%20a%20Delhi%20court%20ordered%20the%20Delhi%20police%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fnews-updates%2Fdelhi-court-release-electronics-devices-editors-the-wire-238549%5C%22%3Ereturn%20the%20seized%20electronic%20devices%20owned%20by%20journalists%20at%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20almost%20a%20year%20after%20the%20crime%20branch%20conducted%20raids%20at%20its%20office%20in%20a%20defamation%20case.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%20kept%20arguing%20for%20almost%20a%20year%20that%20it%20needed%20more%20time%20to%20examin