ld-latin-america-67281584.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%3A%20The%20Who%E2%80%99s%20Who%20in%20the%20Data%20%7C%20Santrash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01093258%2Fa-street-in-Bihar-s-Belchhi-Photo-Ajoy-Ashirwad-Final.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBeyond%20politics%2C%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20is%20a%20revolutionary%20document.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20public%20document%2C%20the%20first%20ever%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Santrash.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%202%2C%20when%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20additional%20chief%20secretary%20Vivek%20Kumar%20Singh%20released%20the%20first%20instalment%20of%20the%20caste-based%20survey%20report%2C%20it%20undoubtedly%20created%20a%20stir%20in%20political%20circles.%20This%20report%20gave%20a%20new%20edge%20to%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20attack%20on%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20called%20for%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fgreater-population-greater-right-rahul-gandhi-hails-bihars-caste-census-101696257725285.html%5C%22%3Egreater%20population%2C%20greater%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20was%20on%20the%20back%20foot%2C%20started%20claiming%20that%20it%20did%20not%20oppose%20the%20caste-based%20enumeration%20in%20Bihar.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20well-known%20that%20when%20leaders%20of%20various%20political%20parties%20in%20Bihar%20led%20by%20Nitish%20Kumar%20demanded%20a%20country-wide%20caste%20census%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20response%20was%20negative.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20354px)%2085vw%2C%20354px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22354%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22507%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20political%20corridors%2C%20the%20report%20has%20raised%20many%20questions%20for%20ethnography%20enthusiasts%20and%20sociologists.%20A%20major%20question%20is%20regarding%20the%20castes%20which%20were%20mentioned%20in%20the%20census%20report%20of%201931%20or%20the%20reports%20of%20the%20Kaka%20Kalelkar%20Commission%20or%20Mandal%20Commission.%20One%20such%20caste%20is%20Santrash.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20caste-based%20occupation%20associated%20with%20Santrash%20is%20carving%20stones%20with%20an%20iron%20chisel%20and%20hammer.%20They%20are%20also%20called%20Sangtarash%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%20From%20a%20linguistic%20point%20of%20view%2C%20the%20name%20of%20the%20caste%20is%20also%20quite%20interesting.%20Both%20Sang%20and%20Tarash%20are%20Persian%20words%3A%20Sang%20means%20stone%20while%20Tarash%20means%20carver.%20But%20it%20is%20not%20a%20Muslim%20caste.%20They%20are%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20evidence%20on%20whether%20older%20generations%20of%20these%20stone%20masons%20have%20worked%20in%20palaces%2C%20forts%20and%20temples%20built%20across%20the%20country.%20But%20it%20can%20be%20said%20that%20they%20must%20have%20played%20a%20role%20and%20at%20one%20point%20they%20must%20have%20been%20spread%20all%20over%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20this%20caste%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20extinction.%20It%20can%20be%20estimated%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20people%20hailing%20from%20this%20caste%20now%20live%20only%20in%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Nawada%20district%2C%20and%20they%20have%20a%20surprisingly%20minuscule%20population.%20In%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20caste%20survey%2C%20only%20287%20people%20in%20Nawada%20district%20claimed%20to%20hail%20from%20the%20Santrash%20caste.%20However%2C%20a%20caste%20survey%20in%20other%20states%20like%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Jharkhand%20and%20West%20Bengal%20would%20be%20able%20to%20offer%20more%20information%20about%20this%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhether%20the%20Santrash%20of%20Bihar%20or%20Sangtarash%20of%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20their%20traditional%20profession%20is%20the%20same%20%E2%80%93%20carving%20stones.%20The%20development%20of%20traditional%20professions%20can%20make%20the%20study%20of%20history%20interesting%20and%20useful%2C%20although%20very%20little%20work%20has%20been%20done%20in%20this%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20question%20is%2C%20what%20do%20people%20of%20these%20castes%20do%20now%3F%20Since%20other%20people%20also%20engage%20in%20stone%20carving%20and%20it%20has%20now%20become%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20sculpting%2C%20not%20everyone%20can%20be%20called%20a%20stone%20carver%20or%20a%20Sangtarash.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20call%20themselves%20Santrash%20still%20earn%20their%20livelihood%20by%20carving%20stones.%20They%20make%20stone%20slabs%2C%20on%20which%20women%2C%20especially%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20grind%20spices%20and%20chutneys.%20But%20they%20abstain%20from%20revealing%20their%20caste%20publicly.%20They%20live%20like%20nomads%2C%20but%20are%20not%20a%20nomadic%20tribe.%20Since%20this%20is%20a%20caste%20that%20is%20also%20involved%20in%20the%20business%20and%20trade%20of%20stone%20slabs%20and%20statues%2C%20they%20prefer%20to%20hide%20their%20caste.%20In%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20they%20identify%20themselves%20as%20the%20Beldar%20caste%2C%20whose%20traditional%20job%20is%20to%20cut%20the%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHiding%20their%20caste%20identity%20is%20probably%20a%20major%20reason%20why%20the%20population%20of%20this%20caste%20is%20dwindling%20in%20Bihar%20and%20is%20limited%20to%20287%20members%20in%20Nawada%20district%20alone.%20The%20Bihar%20government%20has%20categorised%20them%20as%20an%20extremely%20backward%20class%2C%20while%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20they%20are%20a%20backward%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20here%20are%20some%20questions%20that%20remain%3A%20Where%20have%20the%20Sangtarash%20of%20other%20states%20gone%3F%20What%20happened%20to%20their%20traditional%20art%3F%20Will%20the%20government%20of%20this%20country%20ever%20try%20to%20find%20out%20about%20them%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENawal%20Kishor%20Kumar%20is%20the%20Hindi%20editor%20of%20Forward%20Press%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260200%2Fbihar-caste-survey-who-are-the-santarash%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20part%20one%20of%20the%20series%2C%20on%20the%20Ghasi%20community%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20series%20is%20available%20in%20Hindi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260200%2Fbihar-caste-survey-who-are-the-santarash%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20in%20Urdu%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewireurdu.com%2Fauth