2%80%9CThe%20home%20is%20inclusive%2C%20meaning%20there%20are%20no%20separate%20units%20based%20on%20abilities.%20Their%20lives%20matter%20and%20we%20intend%20to%20be%20a%20model%20of%20what%20can%20be%20done.%20Inclusion%20made%20us%20a%20home%2C%20a%20family%2C%20not%20an%20institution%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%20Dr%20Michelle%20has%20faced%20several%20challenges.%20Initially%2C%20she%20had%20to%20fight%20the%20local%20men%20who%20wanted%20a%20key%20to%20the%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20saw%20it%20as%20a%20public%20property%20and%20were%20especially%20angry%20that%20a%20foreigner%20lived%20here.%20There%20were%20rumours%20that%20I%20was%20raising%20the%20girls%20in%20order%20to%20sell%20them%20for%20a%20higher%20price%20abroad.%20I%20was%20given%20death%20threats%20as%20I%20refused%20to%20hire%20people%20working%20under%20a%20political%20umbrella%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20warned%20that%20I%20was%20making%20people%20uneasy%20and%20that%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20safe%20for%20me.%20I%20was%20told%20to%20stop%20and%20leave.%20Of%20course%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t.%20Those%20criminals%20were%20why%20I%20was%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%20the%20octogenarian%20says%20that%20there%20is%20no%20other%20place%20that%20she%20would%20rather%20be%20at.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20succession%20plan%20which%20includes%20the%20girls%20taking%20a%20greater%20role%20in%20the%20operation%20of%20Shishur%20Sevay.%20I%20love%20what%20I%E2%80%99m%20doing%20and%20feel%20blessed%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20it.%20India%20is%20now%20my%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Dr%20Michelle%20Harrison.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698419195000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333185%22%2