abad%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20to%20take%20his%20mother%20on%20a%20ride%20in%20his%20shiny%20new%20SUV%20(sport%20utility%20vehicle).%20However%2C%20little%20did%20he%20anticipate%20that%20this%20journey%20from%20Moradabad%20to%20New%20Delhi%20would%20change%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20driving%20to%20Delhi%20for%20a%20family%20function%2C%20the%20duo%20headed%20to%20Karol%20Bagh.%20Dhananjaya%20struggled%20to%20find%20a%20parking%20spot%20in%20the%20busy%20shopping%20area.%20After%20searching%20for%20more%20than%2020%20minutes%2C%20he%20eventually%20found%20a%20parking%20lot%20belonging%20to%20the%20North%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20(MCD).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeeing%20the%20logo%2C%20I%20thought%20that%20it%20must%20be%20safe.%20The%20parking%20staff%20wanted%20me%20to%20leave%20the%20key.%20I%20was%20apprehensive%20but%20obliged%20after%20seeing%20that%20everyone%20was%20doing%20the%20same.%20I%20took%20my%20parking%20slip%20and%20left%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dhananjaya%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20two-hour%20shopping%20sojourn%2C%20what%20he%20saw%2C%20or%20rather%20didn%E2%80%99t%20see%2C%20made%20the%20ground%20beneath%20his%20feet%20sink.%20His%20car%20was%20nowhere%20to%20be%20seen.%20When%20the%20staff%20there%20seemed%20indifferent%2C%20the%20former%20deputy%20commandant%20knew%20that%20%E2%80%9Csomething%20bad%20had%20happened%E2%80%9D.%20After%20some%20calls%20to%20the%20police%2C%20they%20found%20out%20that%20the%20car%20had%20been%20towed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20car%20was%20damaged%20and%20I%20had%20to%20pay%20more%20than%20Rs%201.75%20lakh%20to%20repair%20it.%20When%20I%20confronted%20the%20parking%20staff%2C%20they%20pointed%20me%20to%20these%20words%20on%20the%20parking%20slip%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98parking%20at%20owner%E2%80%99s%20risk%E2%80%99.%20I%20knew%20that%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20the%20only%20person%20facing%20this%20problem%20and%20harassment%20by%20the%20parking%20mafia%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2034-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EConfronted%20with%20persistent%20parking%20issues%20in%20busy%20areas%20throughout%20the%20country%2C%20he%20spoke%20to%20his%20friend%20Abhimanyu%20Singh.%20This%20discussion%20spurred%20them%20to%20devise%20a%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20ParkMate.%20This%20app-based%20platform%20provides%20hyperlocal%20and%20on-demand%20parking%20solutions%20for%20businesses%20and%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESolving%20the%20parking%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-12-1698415837.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Parkmate%20makes%20parking%20easier%20through%20technology%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-12-1698415837.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-12-1698415837-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-12-1698415837-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-12-1698415837-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-12-1698415837-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333164%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EParkmate%20offers%20a%20%E2%80%98Drop%20and%20Shop%E2%80%99%20service%20for%20customers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20article%20by%20The%20Patriot%2C%20Delhi%20alone%20witnesses%20approximately%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323849%2Fbengaluru-gagandeep-reehal-gursimran-kalra-ai-mobility-startup-built-zpod-driverless-car%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20crore%20cars%20%3C%2Fa%3Eparked%20daily%2C%20contributing%20to%20a%20market%20worth%20Rs%2044.5%20crore.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20receives%20over%20250%20calls%20every%20day%2C%20concerning%20fights%20related%20to%20parking.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDhananjaya%20and%20Abhimanyu%2C%20who%20were%20both%20working%20with%20the%20Government%20at%20the%20time%2C%20decided%20to%20write%20a%20technical%20paper%20about%20the%20parking%20problem%20in%20the%20country.%20But%20their%20research%20led%20them%20to%20find%20a%20long-term%20viable%20solution%20to%20the%20problem%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20that%2097%20percent%20of%20this%20parking%20industry%20is%20unorganised.%20Traffic%20congestion%20leads%20to%20a%20Rs%201.45%20lakh%20crore-worth%20economic%20opportunity%20loss%20in%20four%20major%20cities%20of%20India.%20Of%20this%2C%20Rs%2036%2C000%20crore%20is%20due%20to%20parking%20congestion.%20A%20person%20burns%20100%20litres%20of%20fuel%20searching%20for%20parking%20daily%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dhananjaya%2C%20CEO%20and%20co-founder%2C%20ParkMate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20the%20data%2C%20the%20friends%20decided%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20themselves%20with%20ParkMate%2C%20which%20offers%20two%20solutions%20%E2%80%94%20DASH%20(Drop%20and%20Shop)%20for%20individuals%20and%20the%20Trident%20system%20for%20businesses%20for%20parking%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20access%20the%20DASH%20service%2C%20users%20can%20download%20the%20application%2C%20enter%20the%20destination%2C%20book%20a%20valet%2C%20and%20reach%20there.%20ParkMate%E2%80%99s%20attendants%2C%20who%20are%20OTP%20verified%2C%20will%20pick%20up%20the%20car%20from%20the%20set%20location.%20Dhananjaya%20says%20that%20all%20cars%20are%20GPS-tagged%2C%20enabling%20users%20to%20track%20their%20vehicle%E2%80%99s%20live%20movement.%20They%20also%20share%20360-degree%20images%20of%20the%20cars%20before%20and%20after%20delivery%20with%20the%20customers.%20Once%20done%2C%20you%20can%20tap%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98Get%20my%20car%E2%80%99%20option%20on%20the%20app%2C%20and%20collect%20the%20car%20wherever%20you%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20offer%20instant%2C%20safe%2C%20and%20guaranteed%20parking.%20At%20ParkMate%2C%20the%20risk%20is%20ours%2C%20not%20the%20owner%E2%80%99s.%20We%20cover%20all%20risks%20with%20five%20different%20kinds%20of%20insurance%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParkMate%20charges%20Rs%2049%20for%20its%20services%20plus%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330313%2Fnawgati-fuelling-management-app-innovative-startup-shark-tank-india-bits-pilani%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparking%20charges%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20hire%20any%20staff%20on%20the%20ground%20but%20work%20with%20existing%20parking%20operators.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20with%20the%20official%20operators%20under%20a%20revenue-sharing%20model.%20We%20train%20the%20attendants%20for%2012%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20further%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20businesses%20like%20malls%2C%20shopping%20complexes%2C%20big%20residential%20societies%20and%20government%20offices%2C%20they%20offer%20a%20suite%20of%20software%20and%20hardware%20services%20to%20automate%20parking%20space%20through%20the%20Trident%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20system%20offers%20a%20three-tier%20integration%20of%20the%20FASTag%20plus%20ANPR%20(automatic%20number%20plate%20recognition)%20plus%20UniPay%20system%20(online%20payment%20for%20businesses)%2C%20which%20utilises%20state-of-the-art%20HD%20cameras%2C%20an%20inbuilt%20controller%2C%20and%20our%20proprietary%20software.%20Money%20is%20deducted%20through%20FASTag%20and%20license%20plates%20are%20scanned%20on%20entry%20and%20exit%2C%20making%20vehicle%20entry%20management%20effortless%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhimanyu%20Singh%2C%20co-founder%2C%20ParkMate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParkMate%E2%80%99s%20transactions%20are%20totally%20paperless.%20The%20founders%20say%20their%20goal%20is%20to%20reduce%20congestion%2C%20save%20fuel%2C%20and%20provide%20a%20hassle-free%20parking%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%20July%202022%2C%20ParkMate%20is%20present%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Jaipur%20and%20Lucknow.%20The%20duo%20share%20that%20they%20have%20served%20over%205.5%20lakh%20customers%20so%20far%2C%20and%20are%20launching%20their%20services%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20seven%20more%20cities%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20faced%20a%20frustrating%20time%20parking%20at%20Connaught%20Place%2C%20Karol%20Bagh%2C%20and%20other%20busy%20areas%20in%20Delhi.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20spent%20over%2015%20to%2020%20minutes%20every%20time%20just%20looking%20for%20a%20spot.%20Dealing%20with%20the%20staff%20on%20the%20ground%20is%20also%20a%20tough%20task.%20ParkMate%20has%20really%20simplified%20it%20and%20made%20my%20outings%20fun.%20Their%20interface%20is%20easy%20to%20use%20and%20smooth%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aditya%2C%20a%20ParkMate%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20a%20calculated%20risk%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-11-1698415838.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ParkMate%20offer%20a%20Trident%20service%20for%20businesses%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-11-1698415838.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-11-1698415838-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-11-1698415838-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-11-1698415838-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-11-1698415838-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333165%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EParkMate%20offers%20a%20Trident%20service%20for%20businesses.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENurturing%20this%20idea%20since%202017%2C%20the%20pair%2C%20who%20initially%20met%20as%20teenagers%20at%20a%20Call%20of%20Duty%20(video%20game)%20World%20tournament%2C%20devoted%20time%20to%20refining%20their%20solution%20and%20saving%20funds%20before%20quitting%20their%20jobs.%20Coming%20from%20middle-class%20families%2C%20they%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20taking%20a%20calculated%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20hail%20from%20operational%20backgrounds.%20We%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20corpus%20that%20could%20sustain%20us%20for%20two%20years%20before%20leaving%20our%20jobs.%20Even%20then%2C%20my%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330237%2Fnellayapan-b-kanniyakumari-osd-to-nagaland-chief-minister-inspiring-story-went-viral-on-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20was%20not%20happy%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20me%20quitting%20my%20government%20job.%20We%20suffered%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EAbba%20nahi%20maanenge%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(Dad%20won%E2%80%99t%20agree)%20syndrome.%20My%20parents%20are%20still%20angry%2C%20but%20I%20know%20they%E2%80%99ll%20come%20around%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dhananjaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20say%20that%20they%20did%20not%20draw%20a%20salary%20for%20the%20first%2014%20months%2C%20and%20initially%2C%20they%20faced%20challenges%20in%20convincing%20customers%20and%20finding%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20industry%20is%20dominated%20by%20the%20mafia.%20It%E2%80%99s%20tough%20to%20approach%20them%20and%20seek%20a%20partnership.%20Moreover%2C%20we%20started%20our%20company%20during%20a%20funding%20winter%20(a%20time%20when%20venture%20capital%20was%20less)%20and%20had%20to%20pool%20in%20our%20own%20savings.%20The%20biggest%20challenge%20though%2C%20was%20educating%20people%20about%20our%20services%20and%20gaining%20their%20trust.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%20advertisements%20for%20the%20same%20but%20have%20worked%20on%20building%20their%20trust%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dhananjaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheir%20goal%20is%20now%20to%20expand%20across%20the%20country%20and%20become%20the%20go-to%20parking%20solution%20for%20Indians.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20anyone%20to%20worry%20about%20parking%20when%20they%20go%20out.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20have%20a%20good%20time.%20The%20risk%20is%20on%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthepatriot.in%2Freports%2Fdelhis-mega-parking-crisis-10121%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Delhi%E2%80%99s%20mega%20parking%20crisis%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20Published%20on%2021%20June%2C%202019%20Courtesy%20The%20Patriot%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698416550000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FMy-work-view-12-1698415837.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333159%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Based%20in%20Delhi%2C%20friends%20Dhananjaya%20Bharadwaj%20and%20Abhimanyu%20Singh%20founded%20%E2%80%98ParkMate%E2%80%99%20to%20tackle%20parking%20challenges%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333159%2Fdelhi-startup-dhananjaya-bharadwaj-abhimanyu-singh-parkmate-find-parking-app%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ISRO%20Announces%20Free%20Online%20Certification%20Course%20In%20GIS%20%26amp%3B%20Remote%20Sensing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Remote%20Sensing%20(IIRS)%2C%20a%20division%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F308574%2Fchennai-space-tech-startup-agnikul-behind-indias-first-3d-printed-rockets-isro-launchpad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20recently%20unveiled%20an%20opportunity%20for%20individuals%20interested%20in%20advancing%20their%20knowledge%20in%20Remote%20Sensing%2C%20Geographical%20Information%20System%20(GIS)%2C%20and%20Global%20Navigation%20Satellite%20System%20(GNSS)%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20certification%20course%20is%20designed%20to%20cater%20to%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20participants%2C%20including%20students%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332918%2Fisro-announces-job-openings-for-scientists-salaries-up-to-rs-79662-per-month%2F%5C%22%3Etechnical%20and%20scientific%20personnel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20university%20faculty%2C%20researchers%2C%20and%20professionals%20in%20related%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThings%20to%20know%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20programme%20covers%20the%20practical%20application%20of%20remote%20sensing%20and%20GIS%20in%20various%20sectors%20%E2%80%94%20including%20agriculture%2C%20forestry%2C%20ecology%2C%20geoscience%2C%20marine%20and%20atmospheric%20sciences%2C%20urban%20and%20regional%20studies%2C%20and%20water%20resources.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EParticipants%20will%20have%20access%20to%20PDF%20lectures%2C%20recorded%20video%20lectures%2C%20open-source%20software%2C%20and%20demonstration%20handouts%2C%20accessible%20via%20the%20E-CLASS%20and%20ISRO%20Learning%20Management%20System.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThere%20are%20a%20total%20of%2010%2C000%20seats%20available%20for%20the%20entire%20comprehensive%20course%2C%20and%205%2C000%20more%20seats%20for%20individual%20modules.%20Additionally%2C%20nodal%20centre%20coordinators%20are%20allocated%2025%20seats%20for%20each%20course.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EParticipants%20will%20get%20a%20course%20completion%20certificate%20on%20completing%20at%20least%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20session%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20apply%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EUndergraduate%20and%20postgraduate%20students%20(any%20year)%2C%20technical%20and%20scientific%20staff%20from%20central%20or%20state%20governments%2C%20faculty%20and%20researchers%20from%20universities%20and%20institutions%2C%20and%20other%20professionals%20in%20technical%20and%20scientific%20domains.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EInterested%20individuals%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Felearning.iirs.gov.in%2Fedusatregistration%2Fstudent%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregister%20individually%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20through%20their%20respective%20nodal%20centres%20before%20the%20application%20deadline.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EImportant%20dates%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3ECourse%20duration%3A%206%20to%2017%20November%2C%202023%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ERegistration%20open%20date%3A%2016%20October%2C%202023%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ERegistration%20closing%20date%3A%203%20November%2C%202023%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20more%20details%2C%20check%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iirs.gov.in%2Fiirs%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2F2023%2FBrochure_of_122th_Course.pdf%5C%22%20target%3